    mi "そうだね～！　それに、ひっちゃんは自分の考えでわたしたちを手伝うって決めたわけだから…… わたしはゆっくりできるってわけ！　ラッキーだよね～、ね？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1749
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_6978a8e0:

    # "I open my mouth to say something but then realize there's no point."
    "俺は何か言おうと口を開くが、何の意味もないことに気づく。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1751
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_66d63d19:

    # "I refocus on trying to think of a way out of this. No, their actions are clearly deliberate, there's no sense in attempting to reason with them."
    "この状況から抜け出す手を考えることに集中する。いや、こいつらの行動は明らかにわざとだ。理屈で攻めるのは全くの無駄だ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1753
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_127b6e4f:

    # "You can't reason with madmen. I frown, and they don't even notice my discontent, further proving my suspicions."
    "狂人には理屈は通じない。俺はしかめ面をするが、二人は俺の不満に気づきもしない。いよいよもって怪しい。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1755
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_19958ec4:

    # "They seem pretty relaxed now. I guess they think they've already won, so they're letting their guard down."
    "二人ともかなり落ち着いて見える。もう勝ったと思って、油断してるんだろう。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1759
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_320b8041:

    # "That's kind of arrogant."
    "ちょっと思い上がりじゃないか。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1761
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_bd6922f7:

    # "They pass forward in front of me as they move through the doorway,"
    "二人は俺の前を通って、ドアから外に出る。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1767
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_d64efd7f:

    # "And I stealthily walk backwards back into the classroom as they step into the hallway, turning towards the stairwell."
    "そのまま廊下に出て階段に向かうのを見つつ、俺はこっそりと教室側に逆戻りする。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1769
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_2a9b5659:

    # "I let out a sigh of relief and quickly pack the rest of my stuff so I can make my escape."
    "安堵のため息をつくと、この場から脱出するために急いで荷物をまとめる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1773
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_9633655f:

    # "The classroom door slams shut."
    "教室のドアがバタンと閉じる。"

