    mi "うんうん、そうだよね……ははは！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1802
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_78cf42b8:

    # mi "What was that about? I thought you said you'd help us!"
    mi "今のはどういうつもり？　手伝ってくれるって言ったじゃない！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1804
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_8f23651e:

    # mi "And then you bailed on us! And you thought you would get away with it, didn't you?"
    mi "それなのに逃げ出すような真似して！　それで許されるって思ってたんだよね、そうでしょ！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1809
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_aa330ff2:

    # "The indignant expression vanishes and she begins to laugh hysterically, calming down only after an aggravated look from Shizune."
    "怒った表情が消え失せ、ミーシャはげらげらと笑いだして止まらなくなる。静音のいらだった視線を受けて、ようやく落ち着く。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1814
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_0dd4a414:

    # mi "Oh, ah… Yeah~, you thought you could get away with it! But, a criminal always returns to the scene of the crime!"
    mi "ぜー、はー……いや～、ほんとに逃げられると思ってたんだね！　でも、犯人は必ず犯行現場に戻ってくるものだよね！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1816
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_c8b67a8d:

    # "I didn't even manage to leave the classroom in the first place. No, wait, I didn't even agree to help in the first place."
    "俺はそもそも教室から出てないぞ。いや待て、それ以前に手伝うなんて言ってもいないじゃないか。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1821
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_486895ba:

    # mi "Not very bright, are you, criminal? Thinking you can just shirk your duties like that… How low, Hicchan~!"
    mi "あまり頭は良くないみたいね、犯罪者さん。そんなふうに仕事をさぼろうとして……卑劣だよ、ひっちゃん～！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1823
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_9db96e46:

    # hi "I'm a criminal? What did I do? What's the charge? What am I guilty of?"
    hi "俺は犯罪者かよ？　俺が何をしたって言うんだ？　容疑は何だよ？　何か悪いことしたか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1828
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_3356e3b9:

    # mi "That's for the courts to decide, criminal! I don't think we have to tell you that!"
    mi "それは裁判所が決めることよ、犯罪者さん！　そんなことは言うまでもありません！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1833
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_688e0bf0:

    # mi "Besides, you're the criminal here, you know what you did!"
    mi "それに犯人なら、自分がやったことくらいわかってるんじゃないの～！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1835
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_d3431a2c:

    # hi "Have you ever read 'The Trial,' by Kafka?"
    hi "お前、カフカの『審判』って読んだことあるか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1840
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_db2299c7:

    # mi "No, what's that, Hicchan~? What does that have to do with this?"
    mi "んーん、何それ、ひっちゃん～？　それとこれと何の関係があるの？"

