    "なんて気の滅入る……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1949
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_131c5256:

    # mi "Cheer up, cheer up, Hicchan!"
    mi "ほら、元気出してよ、ひっちゃん！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1951
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_58c62dae:

    # "She slaps me hard across the back with enough strength to knock the air out of my lungs. I gasp to breathe."
    "ミーシャが思い切り俺の背中をぶっ叩く。肺から空気が押し出されてしまい、俺は息を切らして喘ぐ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1953
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_72988eba:

    # mi "Besides, aren't you happy you get to spend the day with two cute girls?"
    mi "それに、こんなにかわいい女の子二人といっしょにいられるのに、うれしいと思わないの？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1958
