    mi "今のは黙ってたほうがよかったかもね。ひっちゃんに知恵をつけることになっちゃうから～"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2079
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_c5e7ae88:

    # "But, just the fact that she is all right with telling me this shows me that she doubts I'll be able to act on it."
    "でもわざわざ俺に言っているということは、俺がそんな行動に移れるはずがないと踏んでいることの証拠だ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2081
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_c4c68ce3:

    # "That only makes me want to do it more, and I almost want the opportunity to do so to arise again. But if that happens, she might get me again somehow."
    "そう考えると余計に逃げ出してやりたくなる。そのチャンスが生まれることを期待しさえする。でも仮にチャンスがあっても、静音はまた俺を捕まえるかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2086
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_ef2b123c_20:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2091
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_19ce629b:

    # mi "Shicchan says she is happy now."
    mi "しっちゃんは満足だって"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2100
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_610e1cd4:

    # "Much, much later in the evening, we are looking at six completed stalls."
    "さらに夜遅く、俺たちの前には６つの完成した屋台が並ぶ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2102
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_e143567b:

    # "With the pride of a job well done, we sit back and admire the fruits of our labor, not sharing a word between us. Just admiring."
    "仕事をやりとげた誇らしさとともに、俺たちは座り込んで労働の成果に見とれる。一言も言葉を交わさない。ただ見とれ続ける。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2104
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_5c8c60c6:

    # "I realize I'm feeling quite thirsty."
    "俺はひどくのどが渇いていることに気づく。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2106
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_b4898861:

    # hi "Hey, isn't there a vending machine out in the hall? They're on all day, right?"
    hi "なあ、廊下に自動販売機があったよな？　あれ、２４時間動いてるだろ？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2111
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_e69ed216:

    # mi "Yeah, the drinks are very cheap, too. We usually get something from there on days like this."
    mi "うん、それにすごく安いよ。今日みたいな日はあそこで飲み物買うんだ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2113
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_5c74b984:

    # "I dig around in my pocket, and find a single hundred yen coin."
    "ポケットを探ると、百円玉が一枚見つかる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2115
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_91a5a767:

    # hi "Is this enough? I'm feeling kind of thirsty."
    hi "これで足りる？　俺ちょっとのど渇いたよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2120
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_71d83941:

    # mi "A hundred yen? You can get any drink in the machine with that."
    mi "百円？　それだけあればどれでも買えるよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2122
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_ddd1c0a4:

    # hi "That's good, that's very good, then."
    hi "よかった。そりゃありがたい"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2131
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_ef2b123c_21:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2136
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_7568a39c:

    # mi "Ah, wait a second."
    mi "あ、ちょっと待って"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2141
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_b288c619:

    # mi "Hm? What is it, Shicchan? Do you want him to get you a drink too? Hahaha!"
    mi "んー？　なあに、しっちゃん？　自分の分も買ってきてほしいって？　ははは！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2146
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_ef2b123c_22:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2151
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_437fa538:

    # mi "Hicchan, you've really helped us out, so today I - I mean Shicchan, will treat you."
    mi "ひっちゃん、今日はよく手伝ってくれたから、わたしが――わたしじゃなくてしっちゃんね――おごってあげる"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2156
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_431583a4:

    # mi "Hey, what about me?"
    mi "ちょっと、わたしは？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2161
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_ef2b123c_23:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2166
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_e716fc93:

    # mi "What would you like? I'm feeling thirsty myself?"
    mi "何がほしい？　わたしものどがかわいてるんだ？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2171
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_4e762f9f:

    # mi "So am I!"
    mi "わたしもだよ！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2173
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_7955e63e:

    # hi "Hm, I don't know. Anything's fine. I guess the melon soda."
    hi "うーん、どうだろう。何でもいいよ。メロンソーダとか"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2178
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_ef2b123c_24:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2183
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_db58fee4:

    # mi "Hey, wait, Shicchan! I also want a drink!"
    mi "ちょっと待ってよ、しっちゃん！　わたしも飲み物ほしい！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2192
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_e470b5eb:

    # mi "Aw…!"
    mi "あーあ……！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2197
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_a8a92f68:

    # mi "You know, it's times like this that I think she is just teasing me."
    mi "なんか、こういうときって単にからかわれてるんじゃないかって気がするんだよね"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2199
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_09c00868:

    # hi "That's probably it. I'm sure she'll get you something, right?"
    hi "まあそうなんだろうな。ちゃんとお前にも買ってきてくれると思うよ。そうだろ？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2201
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_d0eedc89:

    # mi "Yeah, she usually does. But… you never know…"
    mi "うん、いつもは買ってきてくれるけど……わかんないよね……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2203
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_adba988c:

    # hi "Heh."
    hi "ふーん"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2212
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_7ab1ea70:

    # "Shizune comes back with two melon sodas and a can of fruit juice."
    "静音はメロンソーダ二つと、フルーツジュースを持って戻ってくる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2214
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_b65a1284:

    # "She hands me one of the sodas, and the other to Misha."
    "メロンソーダを一つ俺に、もう一つをミーシャに渡す。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2219
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_74c350eb:

    # mi "Thanks, Shicchan~! I had total faith that you'd get me one, I knew I could count on you! Wahahaha!"
    mi "ありがと、しっちゃん～！　わたしにも買ってきてくれるって信じてたよ、やっぱ頼りになるね！　わははは！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2224
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_d9c8d388:

    # mi "But how did you know this was what I wanted? I usually get something else."
    mi "でもどうしてわたしが欲しかったのがわかったの？　いつもは違うのを買ってるのに"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2229
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_ef2b123c_25:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2234
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_29ab98ca:

    # mi "What? You knew I'd want to try it? And that I like these kinds of childish things? Hahahaha!"
    mi "なに？　試しに飲みたいと思ってると思った？　それにこういう子供っぽいのが好きだろうって？　はははは！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2239
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_0c538b1a_1:

    # mi "Hahahaha!"
    mi "はははは！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2241
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_b695e458:

    # "I gesture my thanks to Shizune, who smiles and nods."
    "俺は手振りで静音に感謝の気持ちを伝える。静音は笑顔でうなずく。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2246
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_ef2b123c_26:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2253
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_4df21599:

    # mi "Hey, Hicchan…"
    mi "ねえ、ひっちゃん……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2255
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_80452e63:

    # hi "Yes?"
    hi "ん？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2260
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_ef2b123c_27:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2265
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_95f648b0:

    # mi "We've been spending a lot of time together. Already, in such a short time, we've done so much."
    mi "わたしたち、長いこと一緒に過ごしたよね。初めて会ってからほんの少ししか経ってないけど、すごくいろんなことをやりとげてきた"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2267
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_3acbd374:

    # mi "We should both stop beating around the bush. What I'm trying to say is,"
    mi "お互い、そろそろ率直に話すべきだと思う。何が言いたいかっていうと、"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2269
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_2df3d665:

    # "It sounds a lot like she's going to ask me out, but that can't be it. Nevertheless, my heart is beating like a jackhammer. Damn, this reminds me of another similar scene earlier this year."
    "なんだか今にも告白してきそうな口ぶりだけど、まさかそんなはずはないだろう。それでも俺の心臓は削岩機のようにバクバクいっている。くそ、あのときのことを思い出すじゃないか。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2271
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_c245aef2:

    # "I try to say something, but my brains can't decide whether to stop her or to tell her to continue."
    "何か言おうと思うけど、それ以上話すなと言うべきか、そのまま続けろと言うべきか、俺の頭では決められない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2273
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_8753413a:

    # "I feel myself blushing all the way to the ears."
    "耳まで真っ赤になるのが自分でもわかる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2278
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_ef2b123c_28:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2283
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_c0bbc816:

    # mi "What I'm trying to say is…"
    mi "何が言いたいかっていうと……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2290
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_b5f5489a:

    # mi "Would you like to join the Student Council?"
    mi "生徒会に入る気はない？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2292
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_0d5042d4:

    # hi "Ah, what a disappointment."
    hi "何だよ、つまらないな"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2298
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_7e938a87:

    # mi "Hahaha! Hahahaha! Hahahahaha! Wahaha! Hahahaha!"
    mi "ははは！　はははは！　ははははは！　わはは！　はははは！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2300
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_41eccc07:

    # mi "Did you think she wanted to ask you out, Hicchan?"
    mi "しっちゃんに告白されると思ってたの、ひっちゃん？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2302
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_3b829d95:

    # mi "Hahahaha! Hahaha! Hahaha! Hahahaha!"
    mi "はははは！　ははは！　ははは！　はははは！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2304
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_0cce34d1:

    # mi "Hahahahahahahaha!"
    mi "はははははははは！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2306
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_8841d736:

    # "I feel very embarrassed right now, I can feel myself getting even redder in the face."
    "俺は今、とても恥ずかしい。顔がさらに赤くなるのを感じる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2308
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_ef06b635:

    # "Shizune also tries to hide a blush after Misha translates, and then puts a few sheets of paper in front of me."
    "ミーシャの翻訳を見て、静音も赤面するのを隠そうとしている。そして数枚の紙を俺の前に差し出す。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2313
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_ef2b123c_29:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2318
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_2d21ba26:

    # mi "So, how about it? All the paperwork is right here."
    mi "で、どうなの？　書類は全部用意してあるわ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2323
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_945748c6:

    # mi "And you are sitting down, anyway. You look very at home here. Drinks and everything~!"
    mi "あなたもちょうど席に着いてるし、くつろいでるみたいだし。飲み物とかいろいろね～！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2328
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_ef2b123c_30:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2333
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_2db66125:

    # mi "What do you say?"
    mi "どう？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2335
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_dbbda9dd:

    # "She quiets down a little and asks again a little more solemnly."
    "ミーシャはしばらく黙り込み、もう少し真剣な調子で聞き直す。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2340
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_e15f536e:

    # mi "Hicchan, what do you say?"
    mi "ひっちゃん、どうなの？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2345
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_b4b48a46:

    # mi "You don't exactly hate this, right?"
    mi "そこまでイヤだってわけでもないんでしょ？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2347
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_3e8d96f9:

    # "I'm more than a little surprised by this sudden change of tone. I don't really know how to react to it."
    "急な態度の変わりぶりにとても驚く。どう反応すればいいのか、正直よくわからない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2349
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_63f33670:

    # "For one thing, she isn't shouting uproariously with no regard for tact."
    "まず、いつものような遠慮なしの騒がしい叫び声じゃない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2351
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_309e4daa:

    # "Before, I'm sure she knew already that I was going to say no."
    "今までは、ミーシャは俺が断るのをわかっていてやっていたと思う。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2353
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_d138a6ef:

    # "This time, she seems actually serious."
    "今度はどうやら本当に真剣みたいだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2358
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_129b1dc6:

    # mi "I think maybe you should join. Not just because we could use your help, but, well, you're hanging out with us anyway."
    mi "わたしは、ひっちゃんは生徒会に入るべきだと思ってる。手伝ってもらえると助かるからってだけじゃなくて、その、どっちみちわたしたちと一緒に過ごしてるわけだし"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2360
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_fb616d18:

    # mi "I think Shicchan would like it if you would join as well. It's not like you hate us or anything, right?"
    mi "ひっちゃんが生徒会に入ってくれたら、しっちゃんも喜ぶと思う。わたしたちのこと、嫌いってわけじゃないんでしょ、ね？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2365
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_d2481fed:

    # mi "It wouldn't hurt if you joined. And I'd appreciate it if you would."
    mi "入ってもひっちゃんには何の損もないよ。それに、わたしも入ってくれたらうれしいよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2367
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_b7cc0115:

    # "She seems to be having a hard time getting her words out, which is strange for someone talkative like Misha."
    "ミーシャはなんだかしゃべりにくそうにしている。普段はあんなにおしゃべりなのに、妙な感じだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2369
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_31a2f574:

    # "For some reason, I'm almost troubled by it."
    "どういうわけか、俺は心配にさえなってくる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2374
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_6faa0438:

    # "My eyes drift over to Shizune, who stares back at me tentatively, absentmindedly cleaning her fingernails."
    "視線を静音のほうに向けると、静音は上の空で爪をいじりながら、ためらいがちに俺を見つめ返す。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2379
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_e8b2f66b:

    # mi "If you don't want to join, I promise we won't ask again, but if you did, we would be really happy."
    mi "入りたくないなら、もう二度と誘わないって約束する。でも入ってくれたら、わたしたちすごく嬉しいな"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2381
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_a2b9d58a:

    # "Both Shizune and Misha seem to be unable to look me in the eye."
    "静音もミーシャも、俺をまっすぐに見られないようだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2383
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_69ac20db:

    # "I can't lie, the thought of being around two such cute girls is something that I couldn't possibly pass up."
    "白状すれば、俺もこんなにかわいい子二人といっしょに過ごせるチャンスを逃すことはできなかった。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2385
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_f603e3ba:

    # "I'm not looking forward to this kind of work every day, but there should be less after the festival."
    "こんな大変な仕事を毎日こなすのは願い下げだけど、学園祭が終われば仕事の量も減るはずだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2387
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_d4f12c8b:

    # "At least, I hope so."
    "少なくともそう願いたい。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2389
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_c2266ff1:

    # hi "All right. I guess it can't hurt, so, why not?"
    hi "わかったよ、損にはならないだろうし、やってみる"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2394
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_ef2b123c_31:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2399
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_1e40c5e0:

    # mi "Wonderful. Wonderful! Ahahaha~!"
    mi "すごい、最高だよ！　あははは～！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2401
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_eeaaa6a8:

    # "Shizune tents her fingers in satisfaction."
    "静音は満足そうに手を合わせる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2406
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_ef2b123c_32:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2411
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_126f6e65:

    # mi "She'll fill everything out, Hicchan. Congratulations, you are officially a member of the Student Council now!"
    mi "書類はしっちゃんが用意してくれるよ、ひっちゃん。おめでとう、これでたった今から正式に生徒会のメンバーだよ！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2413
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_0339b15c:

    # hi "Great. I'm not looking forward to a lot of work."
    hi "そりゃよかった。あまり仕事が多くないといいけどな"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2415
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_34a42b39:

    # hi "To be honest, I've never done any student council activities before."
    hi "正直言うと、今まで生徒会の活動ってものに一度も関わったことがないんだ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2417
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_2be46e3d:

    # hi "But maybe it'll be a positive experience?"
    hi "でもまあ、いい経験にはなるのかな？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2419
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_d23ec9be:

    # "Misha starts to clap, laughing exuberantly as she does."
    "ミーシャはいつものように元気いっぱいに笑いながら、拍手を始める。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2424
