    # hi "I get the message."
    hi "もうわかったよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2449
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_71a0b750:

    # "I can't help but smile, finding such a display childishly cute."
    "子供みたいにかわいらしい振る舞いに、俺は笑いを抑えられない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2454
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_62118345:

    # mi "The Student Council is always busy, you know! But for today, we're done. See you tomorrow, Hicchan!"
    mi "あのね、生徒会はいつも忙しいんだよ！　でも今日のところはおしまい。また明日ね、ひっちゃん！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2459
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_95124506:

    # mi "We still have work left, so we'll be counting on you!"
    mi "まだ仕事はあるんだから、よろしくね！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2466
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_418ddace:

    # "I leave the room, feeling totally wiped out. The grounds are totally deserted, and the school looks pretty ominous this late. The council office is the only window with lights on any more."
    "完全に疲れ切った俺は部屋を出る。運動場は人っ子一人いない。こう遅くなると、学校は不気味な場所に見える。まだ明かりがついているのは生徒会室の窓だけだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2468
translate jp a1_thursday_event_horizon_11656c43:

    # "Is this what the Student Council will be like? My body might not be able to take it."
    "生徒会ってのはこういうものなのか？　これじゃ俺の体はもたないかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2480
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_44eb99a3:

    # "Hanako doesn't come to the morning class at all, leaving her seat looking empty and lonely in the back of the classroom."
    "華子は全く朝の授業に顔を出さない。教室の後ろに残された彼女の席は、からっぽで寂しく見える。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2482
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_3ee2b458:

    # "I have to tell her that Lilly was looking for her if I see her later."
    "後で見かけたら、リリーが探していたって伝えないと。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2484
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_3e419e40:

    # "After the events of this morning, class is pretty boring in comparison. I turn the pages of my textbook lazily."
    "今朝のあの出来事にくらべれば、授業はとても退屈だ。俺はだらだらと教科書のページをめくる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2486
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_7302f1af:

    # "I have a bit of catching up to do, despite trying to keep up with my studies at the hospital, but I'm not feeling that enthusiastic about it."
    "病院でも勉強が遅れないように努力はしていたけど、それでも追いつかなくて結構やることが多い。べつに、特別にやる気があるってわけじゃないけど。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2488
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_74b51abd:

    # "The clock at the front of the room sounds unbearably loud. The teacher hasn't said anything in over seven minutes, instead opting to cover the board in rows and rows of equations taken directly from the book."
    "教室正面にかかった時計の音がうるさくてたまらない。先生はもう７分ほど一言も話していない。かわりに、延々と続く数式を教科書から黒板に丸写ししている。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2490
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_3ed5fdc5:

    # "The rhythmic clashing of chalk on blackboard seems to synchronize perfectly with the ticking of the clock."
    "チョークが黒板にぶつかる規則的な音が、時計の秒針の音に完全に同調しているような気がする。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2492
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_47292f1e:

    # "I start to copy down the equations just to pass the time, even though they are right there in the text book."
    "暇つぶしにその数式をノートに取り始める。といっても、全部教科書に載っているんだけど。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2499
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_c0a370db:

    # "When the bell rings, I'm not in a hurry because I have nothing to do, so I stay for a while, reviewing what we covered in class today. I prefer to leave last anyway, so I don't have to deal with crowding in the hallways."
    "ベルが鳴るけど、特に急いでいるわけではないので、俺はしばらく教室に残ってその日の授業内容を復習する。もともと最後に教室を出るのが好きだった。そのほうが廊下の人混みを避けられるし。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2501
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_1515130e:

    # "I notice Shizune and Misha have also stayed behind, talking to someone from another class."
    "静音とミーシャも残っているのに気づく。他のクラスの誰かと話しているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2503
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_cefe8b96:

    # "Shizune's signing so fast that her hands make noises like swords cutting through the air."
    "静音の手話があまりに早いので、手を動かす際に剣で空気を切っているような音がする。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2505
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_69841580:

    # "Maybe there is pent up anger in there."
    "押し殺した怒りがこもっているのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2507
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_2c9bb7bc:

    # "Misha is trying desperately to keep up, but it's clear she can barely manage to even understand her."
    "ミーシャが必死に追いつこうとしているけど、理解するだけでも精一杯なのが見ていてもわかる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2509
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_812aae5c:

    # "I put my head down. Whatever they're discussing, it looks like serious business."
    "俺はうなだれる。何を話しているのか知らないけど、真剣な話みたいだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2511
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_58fc6a43:

    # "Shizune signs to the point where her wrists crackle, and Misha struggles to spit it out in word form."
    "手話の勢いが激しすぎて、静音の手首がぱきんと鳴る。ミーシャはそれを言葉にして伝えようと悪戦苦闘している。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2513
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_7164b201:

    # "Sometimes she trips over herself like she's dealing with tongue twisters. And then on top of that, she has to sign back anything the other girl says."
    "ときどき、早口言葉を噛んだときのように言い間違える。その上、他の女子の話も静音に訳さないといけない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2515
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_4a6bd3a3:

    # "Seems like a rough job."
    "大変そうだなあ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2517
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_7472ffa8:

    # "Misha looks tired, like she's about to faint."
    "見るからにミーシャは疲れている。今にも倒れそうだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2519
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_5693d774:

    # "Luckily for her, their business is soon finished and the girls sit down on their seats again."
    "幸いなことに話はすぐに終わり、静音とミーシャはまた自分の席に戻る。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2525
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_69b537ad:

    # mi "Uwaaah! I'm so tired!"
    mi "うわああぁ！　つかれたよー！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2527
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_f2b05975:

    # "She's hanging her head limply on her desk, looking exhausted."
    "ミーシャは疲れきった様子で、ぐったりと机に突っ伏す。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2529
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_be458f5c:

    # "I'll use the opportunity to reconcile with Shizune a bit, without getting roped into the student council thing again, though I suspect that door is now closed for me."
    "今なら生徒会に引きずり込まれることなく、少しは静音と仲直りできるチャンスだ。まあ、生徒会に入れる可能性はもうないだろうけど。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2531
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_e28eb4ac:

    # hi "Festival preparations must be tough for you."
    hi "学園祭の準備、大変なんだな"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2533
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_80433201:

    # "Indeed, the people in this school seem to be taking the festival very seriously. Whenever I see people idling around before and after classes they're always talking about their plans for it."
    "確かに、この学校の生徒たちは学園祭にとても真剣に取り組んでいるようだ。授業の合間にその辺をぶらついている生徒を見ても、いつも自分の関わっている企画の話をしている。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2535
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_8c17bdf8:

    # "It's kind of neat to see everyone being so enthusiastic about it."
    "みんながこれだけ熱心になっているというのはすごいな、と思う。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2537
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_59f34f11:

    # "I'm probably the only one who doesn't have something to do."
    "何もやることがない、というのはたぶん俺だけだろう。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2542
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_4533e224:

    # "Shizune scoffs at me first, as if trying to decide whether to ignore or sneer at me, but in the end she starts signing without doing either."
    "静音は鼻で笑う。俺を無視するか冷笑するか考えていたのだろうか。でも結局そのどちらもせず、手話を始める。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2547
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_575f2879:

    # "Misha perks up, looking at her hands with slightly unfocused eyes."
    "ミーシャはそれを見て起きあがり、静音の手を少し焦点のぼけた目で追う。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2552
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2554
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_d3e72a0e:

    # "She signs with harsh, heavy, dramatic strokes."
    "厳しく、重々しく、芝居ががった調子で静音は手を動かす。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2556
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_af11886d:

    # "Misha translates her signing into speech for me."
    "ミーシャがその手話を言葉に訳してくれる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2558
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_edbbf32a:

    # "She does it so well it's almost like Shizune is actually speaking, transmitting her thoughts directly through Misha."
    "ミーシャの訳し方は本当にうまい。静音が実際にしゃべっていて、考えていることを直接ミーシャを通じて伝えているかのようだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2560
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_88603ddd:

    # "She must've practiced it vigorously."
    "きっとがんばって練習したんだろうな。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2565
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_93c04d8d:

    # mi "Well of course, we're in the Student Council, you know, so we're pretty busy."
    mi "そりゃもちろん、わたしたちは生徒会なわけですから。結構忙しいのよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2570
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2575
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_071a9241:

    # mi "It's an important duty of ours, to ensure the success of the festival with all our strength."
    mi "全力を尽くして、学園祭を確実に成功させるのが、わたしたちの大事な務めなの"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2580
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_ef2b123c_2:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2585
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_6024cf23:

    # mi "We would shame ourselves in front of the past student council generations if the festival were to fail."
    mi "もし学園祭が失敗に終わったら、過去の生徒会の先輩たちの目の前で恥をかくことになるわ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2590
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_ef2b123c_3:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2595
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_42f99426:

    # mi "That's why there must be no flaws, no… errr I think that was 'incumbrances,' no nothing that might make the festival short of perfect."
    mi "だから学園祭を不完全なものにしてしまうような間違い、じゃなくて、ええと……今のは『妨げ』だと思う……はいっさいあってはいけないの"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2597
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_9b2093d5:

    # "Shizune's passionate speech and Misha's enacting are really oddly fitting of them."
    "静音の情熱的な演説と、ミーシャの実演は本当にお似合いだ。奇妙なくらいに。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2605
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_ea193b62:

    # mi "Oh? Hello~!"
    mi "おや？　こんちは～！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2620
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_7dace9de:

    # "I look over my shoulder and see Hanako peering timidly into the classroom, most of her body hidden behind the door."
    "肩越しに見ると、華子が扉から顔だけを出して、恐る恐る教室の中をのぞいている。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2626
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_66a20675:

    # mi "Hey! Playing delinquent again?"
    mi "なーに？　また不良ごっこ？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2631
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_017b00f5:

    # "Hanako blushes hard at Misha's straightforward jab, even if it was only in jest."
    "ちょっとからかっただけかもしれないけど、ミーシャの単刀直入な当てこすりに華子の顔が真っ赤に染まる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2637
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_ef2b123c_4:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2646
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_dc2745c8:

    # "Shizune stares at her probingly, causing Hanako to look down and start backing away to the point where only her fingers can be seen wrapped nervously around the edge of the door."
    "静音に探るようにじろじろと見られて、華子はうつむいてじりじりと後ずさる。もう神経質そうにドアの端をつかんでいるその指先しか、こちらからは見えない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2648
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_1d19a7e3:

    # "Maybe she is showing her dislike of Hanako by association of her dislike of Lilly."
    "リリーを嫌っている関係で、華子もまとめて毛嫌いしているのだろうか。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2650
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_41fee559:

    # "It appears so, and Hanako probably knows it as well."
    "たぶんそうなんだろう。それは華子にもわかっているはずだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2652
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_1167497a:

    # hi "What is it, Hanako?"
    hi "どうした、華子？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2657
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_4c40cacd:

    # ha "H… has Lilly been here?"
    ha "あ……あの、リリー、来てませんでしたか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2659
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_6817e8e6:

    # mi "Sorry, haven't seen Satou. She, eh, came by in the morning though."
    mi "悪いけど、砂藤さんならいないよ。あー……朝には来てたけど"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2664
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_dcf10048:

    # "Hanako keeps looking uneasily at Shizune, who stares back at her with her usual studying gaze. What is she trying to do?"
    "華子は落ちつかなげに静音を見つめ続ける。静音もいつもの観察眼で華子をにらみ返す。あいつはいったい何がしたいんだ？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2666
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_caad18a8:

    # "Of course Shizune isn't going to look away, and she is intimidating enough as it is, so I can only imagine how terrified Hanako would be."
    "もちろん静音は目をそらしたりしない。それにあいつ自身がそもそも威圧的だ。華子がどれだけおびえているか、想像するに余りある。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2668
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_c0910f6a:

    # "It is a little uncomfortable, watching Hanako's reaction to Shizune's normal behavior. This is what happens when two people of two different extremes meet, it seems."
    "普段どおりの静音に対する華子の反応を見るのは、ちょっと気の毒になる。両極端の二人が出会うとこうなる、ということなのかも。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2673
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_ae0322e5:

    # ha "Do… do you know where she is?"
    ha "ど……どこにいるか、知りませんか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2678
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_ef2b123c_5:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2683
translate jp a1_thursday_above_and_beyond_7feda52a:

    # mi "If she has any sense in her head, she's in her classroom, working on their festival project. But who knows where that woman is loitering at."
    mi "ちょっとでも常識があるんだったら、自分の教室で学園祭の仕事をしてると思うけど。でもどこかで油を売ってるとしても、知りませんけどね"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2709
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_c4674ee7:

    # hi "You need to find her? She was looking for you in the morning but I guess you have missed each other."
    hi "リリーを探してるの？　今朝君を探してたけど、すれ違いになっちゃったみたいだね"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2711
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_3c896058:

    # "She waits a little without answering the simple question, looking awfully like she's not sure if it's proper to answer such a question."
    "少しの間、華子は言葉に詰まる。その簡単な質問に答えるべきなのか、わからない様子だ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2716
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_0a3cf307:

    # ha "Y…yeah."
    ha "は……はい"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2718
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_10305d24:

    # hi "I can come with you."
    hi "一緒に探そうか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2720
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_78eaa06e:

    # hi "If it's okay."
    hi "もしよかったら、だけど"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2728
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_f5c8613d:

    # "Hanako nods fractionally, still on guard, her shoulders stiff like wood. I get the feeling that she might be more comfortable by herself after all, but it's too late to back off now."
    "まだ気を許してくれてはいないらしく、華子は肩をこわばらせてかすかにうなずく。やっぱり、一人でいるほうがずっと気が楽なんだろう。でも、もう後には引けない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2730
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_77c854f7:

    # "She has this really troubled expression she seems to wear almost constantly, one that makes me constantly be on guard myself. I wonder why."
    "なぜかわからないけど、華子はいつもひどく不安そうな表情をしている。そのおかげで俺まで身構えてしまう。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2732
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_a526c4b5:

    # "I kind of understand why she always seems to be so wary… or maybe more like, why there could be a person like her."
    "華子がいつも気を張っている理由……というか、華子みたいな人が存在する理由が、なんとなくわかる気がする。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2734
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_131aef37:

    # "But I still have no idea how I should act around such a person."
    "でも、そういう人のそばでどう振る舞うべきなのかは、いまだにわからない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2736
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_161a05c1:

    # hi "It's dinnertime soon. Were you planning to eat with Lilly?"
    hi "もうすぐ夕食だね。リリーと一緒に食べようとしてたの？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2744
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_f34450c1:

    # "She nods slightly."
    "華子はかすかにうなずく。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2746
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_ec784675:

    # "So she must have been trying to get in the cafeteria."
    "だとすれば、食堂に入ろうとしていたに違いない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2748
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_c500451c:

    # "Well, there's something of a dinner crowd, just like the cafeteria is crowded during lunch."
    "そしたら、夕食をとっている人たちなんかがいて、昼休みのように混んでいた、と。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2750
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_7d73047c:

    # "It's not as bad because dinnertime is longer than lunch hour, but I can understand why Hanako could be discouraged from going in."
    "夕食の時間は長いから、実際は昼休みより空いているはずだ。でも、どうして華子が入るのを思いとどまったのかはわかる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2752
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_1c0a76d6:

    # "I pick up my bag and we take our leave. Hanako skips a little to meet my initial pace, so I slow down to match her speed."
    "かばんを手に取り、華子と教室を出る。俺の歩くペースに合わせて早足になった華子を見て、速度を落とし、歩調を合わせる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2757
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_9159a672:

    # "It doesn't take long for us to be walking at a comfortable pace down the hallway."
    "すぐにちょうど良い早さで廊下を歩けるようになる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2762
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_09e34e7d:

    # "It almost feels like we're going for a stroll together; something that I can't say I've really done before with a girl."
    "なんだか一緒に散歩しているような気分だ。女の子と散歩したことなんてないけど。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2764
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_bebb1632:

    # "Hanako doesn't seem to be thinking the same thing though. Even though we are walking at the same pace, she never comes within arm's reach of me."
    "華子のほうはそう思っていないらしく、同じペースで歩いてはいても、俺の手の届く範囲にくることはない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2766
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_5258ce5b:

    # "I guess she's still a little uncomfortable around me. Given how shy she is, there doesn't seem to be much helping it, at least for now."
    "まだ俺のそばだと少し落ち着かないらしい。華子の内気さを思えば、仕方ないだろう。少なくとも、今は。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2773
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_a4be9382:

    # "By the time we arrive at the cafeteria, there is not much of a crowd there, but Lilly is nowhere to be seen."
    "食堂に着くころには、もう人混みも少なくなっていたけど、リリーはどこにも見あたらない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2778
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_2c22f641:

    # "Hanako's head sinks even lower than usual."
    "華子は普段よりさらに深くうつむく。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2780
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_bfc22a19:

    # hi "Have you looked somewhere else already?"
    hi "他のところは探してみたの？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2785
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_5df00305:

    # ha "J-just at the library… I was reading…"
    ha "と、図書室だけです……本、読んでたから……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2787
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_8aaad939:

    # "So she does spend the classes she skips at the library."
    "やっぱり、華子は授業をさぼって図書室に行っているのか。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2789
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_5a9539f3:

    # hi "Ah, so not exactly a thorough search then. Well, if I had to guess, she'd be in her own class like Shizune said, right?"
    hi "そうか、じゃあちゃんと調べたわけじゃないんだ。俺だったら、リリーは自分の教室にいると思うな。静音が言ってたみたいに。じゃないか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2794
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_40ca9b49:

    # ha "R-right."
    ha "そ、そうですね"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2799
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_67002822:

    # "With the slightest of nods, Hanako agrees with my reasoning."
    "ほんのちょっぴりうなずいて、華子は賛成する。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2801
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_effa7ec7:

    # "God, she's being so awkward."
    "まったく、やりにくいったらない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2803
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_5cc747e1:

    # "It's like I need double layered silk gloves with padding to even begin interacting with her."
    "華子とやりとりするためには、二枚重ねで詰め物入りのシルクの手袋が必要なんじゃないだろうか。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2805
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_0ecc7df8:

    # "Some small talk might help her become a bit more used to me. It isn't hard to tell that the silence between us is hovering on the edge of both our minds."
    "なんとなく空気がぎこちないのは、お互いに黙っているからだ。なにか世間話でもすれば、ちょっとは俺に慣れてくれるかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2807
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_5c512e4b:

    # hi "So you and Lilly usually hang out together after class, right?"
    hi "それで、いつも放課後はリリーと一緒にいるの？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2812
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_13b7ab07:

    # ha "Y-yes."
    ha "は、はい"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2814
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_dfa3fec4:

    # "I'm not quite sure what I expected from her answer, nor why I even asked the question. That much was rather obvious, after all."
    "どういう答えを期待していたんだろう。それに、何でそんなことを聞いたんだろう。わかりきった事じゃないか。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2816
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_8c0d1f2f:

    # "She doesn't seem like the type to cultivate a social circle, either, so I suspect that Lilly may well be her only friend."
    "華子は積極的に友達を作るタイプではなさそうだ。だから、きっとリリーが唯一の友達なんだろう。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2818
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_2df0d113:

    # hi "Must be a pain being in different classes, I'm guessing."
    hi "クラスが違うとつらいんじゃないか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2820
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_cad1bbc4:

    # "She gives a sharp, almost reflexive nod. Compared to Lilly's careful thought about her actions and speech, Hanako hastens to make her answers as prompt and short as possible."
    "華子はコクコクと条件反射のようにうなずく。リリーのゆったりした物腰や話し方と比べ、華子は返答をできる限り素早く簡潔に言おうとしている。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2825
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_d1223dd3:

    # ha "Lilly… comes by the classroom, though. Even when she's busy…"
    ha "でも、リリー……教室に寄ってくれるんです。忙しい時でも……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2827
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_24f2760b:

    # "She gives a small smile as she says it, evidently appreciating the fact that Lilly goes out of her way to help her."
    "華子はそう言うと小さくほほえむ。リリーが自分を助けようとしてくれることに感謝しているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2829
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_bd7f2827:

    # "It's pretty cute, really. There isn't any need to say more, both of us content that the discussion's reached an end."
    "かわいい笑顔だ。特にこれ以上話すこともなく、この会話が終わったことに二人ともほっとする。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2834
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_bc9c0405:

    # "As we ascend the stairs back to the lobby we are met by a group of students heading downstairs like a school of fish moving from one feeding area to another."
    "ロビーに戻るために二人で階段を上っていると、下りてきた生徒の集団と鉢合わせになる。えさ場に向かう魚の群れのような勢いだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2843
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_3c21d5eb:

    # "They seem to be keeping mostly to themselves, but before I can notice her doing so, Hanako has moved around behind me."
    "向こうはこっちのことなんて気にしていないようだけど、いつの間にか華子は俺の後ろに回っている。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2845
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_066b6271:

    # hi "Hey, are you all right?"
    hi "大丈夫？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2850
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_5f86cdc5:

    # ha "J-just keep going…"
    ha "い、行きましょう……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2857
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_4435f7e7:

    # "The students pass us without as much as a second glance, and Hanako takes up position to my side again as we enter the building, her momentary reprieve from her anxiety all but snatched away."
    "生徒たちはこっちに目を向けることもなく通り過ぎていく。建物に入ると、華子はまた俺の横に陣取る。俺への不安を少しの間忘れていたのに、また元通りだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2863
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_7d17a122:

    # "Even as we climb towards the third floor, she doesn't seem to relax."
    "３階へと上がる間も、華子は気を緩める様子がない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2865
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_5b7dd0e5:

    # "It isn't as if I've never known a shy person before, or even shy girls, but Hanako seems to be pretty far beyond what I'd call normal in her fear of other people."
    "引っ込み思案な人や、内気な女の子にだって会ったことならある。でも華子の持つ他人への恐怖は、それをはるかに超えているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2867
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_7b3ae353:

    # "If it weren't for Lilly acting as a mediator, I doubt Hanako would have even been able to walk beside me like this. She seems to completely shut down in the presence of others."
    "橋渡しになるリリーがいなければ、こんな風に俺の横で歩くことさえできなかったかもしれない。華子は、人前では完全に心を閉ざしてしまうらしい。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2869
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_f98e5c7f:

    # "The rest of the walk up to Lilly's classroom continues in strained silence, while I rue her inability to socialize at all."
    "リリーの教室に向かう間、張り詰めた沈黙が続く。その間、華子の内気さについて考え、かわいそうに思う。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2878
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_5c9b438e:

    # "After we make our way up the stairs, the noise coming from Lilly's classroom is audible from halfway down the hallway. I wasn't expecting such a din at all."
    "３階に上がると、リリーの教室から出ている騒音が廊下にまで聞こえてくる。こんなに騒々しいとは思いもよらなかった。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2880
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_3ed340fc:

    # hi "Well, I guess we found her…"
    hi "どうやら、リリーはここらしいな……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2882
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_af64d869:

    # "This wasn't hard. Did Hanako come here first then come to me for backup, I wonder?"
    "なんだ、簡単じゃないか。もしかして、華子は一度ここに来たけど、やっぱり背中を押してほしくてまた俺のところまで来たんだろうか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2884
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_3b3ac266:

    # "Well, if that's true, then at least she's starting to trust me a little. That can only be a good thing."
    "まあ、もしそうなら、俺を少し信用し始めているってことだけは確かだ。良い傾向に違いない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2886
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_392f28e1:

    # "Eventually, the two of us reach the door to class 3-2. With Hanako less than subtly positioning herself behind me, I open the door."
    "ようやく３－２の教室にたどりつく。露骨に俺の背に隠れる華子とともに、俺はドアを開ける。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2895
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_5048be63:

    # "Inside is a hive of activity, seemingly every student in the class talking at once as they work hurriedly on their separate tasks."
    "中は作業の真っ最中だ。生徒たちがそれぞれ慌ただしく働きながら、一斉に話している。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2897
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_ad05a3da:

    # "Going by the paint cans, decorations and banners being made, it must be for the upcoming school festival."
    "ペンキ缶や、製作中の飾りと垂れ幕を見るに、今度の文化祭の準備に違いない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2899
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_a06eba4d:

    # "I guess my first priority should be finding Lilly…"
    "まずリリーを見つけないと……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2901
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_d57fb2b1:

    # "…{w} There."
    "……{w} いた。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2903
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_e307499f:

    # "Finding her among the din is surprisingly easy, not the least because of her looks."
    "喧騒の中でリリーを見つけるのは驚くほど簡単だ。それは彼女の見た目のせいじゃない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2905
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_1895f92c:

    # "With a couple of students gathered around her as she stands at the front of the class, she seems to be in charge of the preparations, or at least busy organizing them."
    "リリーが教室の前に立っていて、周りに２、３人の生徒が集まっている。どうやら準備作業のリーダーか、まとめ役をしているらしい。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2907
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_c74ef6ff:

    # "Carefully negotiating a path through the various students hunched over the floor for lack of desk space, I raise a hand entirely out of habit as we finally reach Lilly."
    "机が足りないせいで、床の上で様々な生徒たちが背中を丸め、話し合っている。それをすり抜けてリリーの所にたどり着くと、俺はいつもの癖で手を上げる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2909
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_4d5294c9:

    # hi "Hi, Lilly."
    hi "よう、リリー"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2914
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_6d1b4e9b:

    # "She perks her head up as she breaks off talking to a noticeably smaller girl who must be her classmate, trying to listen as best she can."
    "リリーは同級生の背の低い女の子に話しかけるのを止め、なんとか声を聞き取ろうと顔を上げる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2916
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_d699f67c:

    # li "Sorry, who…"
    li "すみません、どなたでしょう……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2918
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_5aab2e03:

    # hi "Ah, sorry. Hisao. I have Hanako too."
    hi "あ、ごめん。久夫だよ。華子も一緒"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2930
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_21ebc511:

    # ha "H-hi."
    ha "う、うん"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2932
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_b9b6207e:

    # "She's pretty skittish. Considering the number of people around, it isn't too hard to work out why."
    "華子はかなりびくびくしている。周りの人数を考えると、もっともなことだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2934
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_b6471006:

    # "Lilly takes a moment's pause to assess the situation before turning to the other student once again."
    "リリーは現状把握のために一息おいてから、さっきの生徒に向き直る。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2939
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_f6c80c15:

    # li "For the moment, just ask Moriya for his advice. Kenji's busy with painting one of the banners already."
    li "しばらくアドバイスは森屋さんにしてもらって下さい。瀬藤くんは垂れ幕の一つに色を着けるので手一杯ですから"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2941
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_3f3107f6:

    # "A quick nod and she bounces off, fingers carefully sliding along the wall's face for orientation."
    "素早くうなずくと、その生徒は去っていく。方向を確認するために、慎重に指を壁に這わせている。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2945
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_cb1a16bd:

    # "Wait… Kenji? That Kenji?"
    "ちょっと待て……瀬藤？　それって健二のことか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2947
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_2ff21161:

    # "I quickly turn about, leaning to the side to see past Hanako."
    "俺は急いで振り返り、華子の向こうを見るために体を傾ける。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2949
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_78d30b03:

    # "Sure enough, in a corner of the room, Kenji's hunched over a sheet of cloth as he paints it. His eyes remain only inches from the brush, reminding me of how close he had to be to make out my face when I met him."
    "案の定、部屋の隅で健二が背を丸めて、一枚の布に色を塗っている。目はハケからほんの数センチのところに留めたままだ。あいつに会った時、俺の顔を見分けるためにどれだけ近づいてきたかを思い出す。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2956
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_d0c15076:

    # li "Sorry about that. Our class doesn't have many students with even partial eyesight, so they're in high demand."
    li "ごめんなさい、このクラスにはちゃんと目が見える方が少なくて。なので、少しでも視力のある方は引っ張りだこなんです"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2958
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_b3536a86:

    # "That's right, class 3-2 was specially for students with poor vision. Preparing for the festival must be pretty arduous for them."
    "そうだ、３－２は特に視力が弱い学生のためのクラスだ。彼らにとって文化祭の準備はとても骨の折れることに違いない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2960
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_d51e50ee:

    # hi "Need a hand? I could give you help if you need some. Maybe Hanako could too."
    hi "手は足りてる？　必要だったら手伝えるかもしれないよ。たぶん、華子も"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2962
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_24c7e468:

    # "A chance to set her mind on something would do her good, but I doubt she has the courage to ask outright. She quickly nods in affirmation afterwards, so I'm confident I made the right move."
    "何かに集中するのは、華子にとって良いことだろう。でも、自分から手伝いを申し出る勇気があるとは思えない。華子がうんうんとうなずくのを見て、その判断は正しかったと確信する。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2964
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_c404d15b:

    # "Lilly gives a noticeable sigh of relief."
    "リリーが安堵のため息をつく。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2969
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_3706b3b6:

    # li "Ah, that's good. This might actually get finished before everyone goes off to dinner, now."
    li "助かります。みんなが夕食に行くまでには、終わらせることができるかもしれませんね"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2974
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_7dd10591:

    # li "Would you be able to help the person painting the main banner? It's a big task for him to do, but nobody else can help."
    li "あの大きな垂れ幕に色を塗っている方の手伝いをお願いできます？　瀬藤くん一人でやるには大仕事なんですが、誰も手伝うことが出来ないんですよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2976
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_5693df74:

    # hi "Kenji? Sure."
    hi "健二と？　わかったよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2981
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_5f01f51b:

    # "She seems surprised that I know him. I can't really blame her."
    "リリーは俺が健二を知っていることに驚いているらしい。無理もない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2983
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_4488c3bc:

    # li "I take it you've met?"
    li "お知り合いなんですか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2985
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_11a17fa8:

    # hi "Our rooms in the dorm are right next to each other. Hard to miss each other, really."
    hi "寮の部屋が隣同士なんだ。お互い、会わないほうが難しいよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2990
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_c5e8f3ae:

    # li "Well, it's good to see you're getting friends so fast."
    li "そうですか。こんなに早くお友達ができるなんて良いことですね"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2992
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_275f4e5b:

    # "Friend… I wonder if that's the right word to use for him."
    "お友達……その言葉を健二に使っていいものか。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2994
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_bf02bf91:

    # "Hanako's silence during the proceedings reminds me of the reason I put her up to helping in the first place."
    "このやりとりの間の華子の沈黙に、手伝いを申し出たそもそもの理由を思い出す。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:2996
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_e91cb4d4:

    # hi "We'll go help him then. He knows what needs doing, right?"
    hi "じゃあ健二を手伝うよ。何をすればいいかはあいつが知ってるんだろ？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3001
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_b7212c7c:

    # li "That's right. Just ask if you have any problems."
    li "ええ。何かあれば聞いてください"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3009
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_825c33a2:

    # "Chorusing in assent, Hanako and I begin another trek across the classroom."
    "わかった、と口をそろえて言い、華子と俺は教室を横切っていく。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3011
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_4ee4b181:

    # "Kenji sits crouched on the floor, his gaze fixed on the white calico in front of him."
    "健二は床にしゃがんでいて、自分の前にある白いキャラコをじっと見ている。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3017
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_0fb745b7:

    # hi "Hey Kenji."
    hi "よう、健二"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3019
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_e4b52599:

    # "…No answer. He continues dragging his paint-soaked brush along the large half-painted kanji that's sketched on the sheet in pencil."
    "……返事はない。シートの上に鉛筆でスケッチされた、半分塗りかけの大きな漢字に、ペンキをつけたハケを走らせている。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3021
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_ec39a21d:

    # hi "Kenji?"
    hi "健二？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3026
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_63b50b3e:

    # ke "Huh? What? Who is it?"
    ke "ん？　なんだ？　誰だよ？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3028
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_f2792d47:

    # "If this is the way he treats class members, it's no small wonder he's working on this alone."
    "こいつのクラスメイトへの接し方がこれなら、一人で作業しているのはまあ当然だろう。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3030
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_6b7be117:

    # hi "It's me. Hisao. From the—{w=.5}{nw}"
    hi "俺だよ、久夫。あっちで―― {w=.5}{nw}"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3032
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_6ab6d9c2:

    # ke "Right, right, I know that, man. What're you doing here, though?"
    ke "ああ、そうだ、そうだな、わかってるよ。でもお前ここで何してんだよ？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3034
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_0a2eb556:

    # "His dismissive attitude annoys me."
    "話を聞こうとしないその態度にカチンとくる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3036
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_b7124e88:

    # "He must be the type to really get focused on his work, hating to be disturbed by anyone until he's done, I suppose."
    "こいつは自分の仕事に熱中するタイプに違いない。自分が終わるまで、誰かに邪魔されるのがいやなんだろう。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3045
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_ae65cb85:

    # "While we talk, the sound of Hanako's footsteps as she walks out from behind me reminds me that she's here."
    "健二との話の途中、後ろから出てくる華子の足音が聞こえ、彼女がここにいることを思い出す。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3047
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_f904a4e3:

    # hi "I was just going to help with the banner. Hanako and I, that is."
    hi "垂れ幕の手伝いをしようとしてただけだよ。華子と俺で"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3052
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_d08f3652:

    # ha "H… Hello…"
    ha "こ……こんにちは……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3057
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_db316280:

    # ke "Oh. Er, hey. I guess that's okay."
    ke "おお。あー……やあ。まあ、いいんじゃないの"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3059
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_e8c1ec7d:

    # "As soon as Hanako enters the equation, his demeanor takes a complete about-face. His sudden faux-hospitality is slightly unsettling."
    "華子が関わってくると、すぐに態度をコロっと変えやがった。こいつの上っ面だけの親切な振る舞いに、寒気を覚える。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3061
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_b1218ffd:

    # "Oh, right. Women. On second thoughts, this may not have been a great idea after all."
    "ああ、わかった。女か。やっぱり、いい考えじゃなかったかもな。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3070
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_aee3306b:

    # "Hanako and I grudgingly set ourselves down on the opposite side of the cloth banner to Kenji, noting the several small paint tins on the ground around it."
    "いやいやながら、華子と俺は垂れ幕を挟んで健二の反対側にしゃがむ。下に置かれたいくつかのペンキ缶に注意する。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3072
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_d5ff6ce1:

    # "Class 3-2… noodle stall?"
    "３－２は……そばの屋台？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3074
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_e81a5add:

    # hi "You guys selling noodles at the festival on Sunday?"
    hi "お前のクラスは日曜の学園祭でそばを売るのか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3079
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_5a0d1a3f:

    # ke "Yeah, some stalls outside. Or something."
    ke "ああ。外でいくつか屋台、とかを"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3081
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_d908f21d:

    # "'Or something?' His noncommittal nature sparks a fair amount of suspicion on my behalf. The task at hand comes first, though."
    "『とかを』だって？　こいつのあいまいな性格のせいで、もやもやした気持ちが生まれる。とは言え、今は作業が最優先だ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3083
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_e9a9517a:

    # hi "So how do you want to split this? We do borders while you do the text? Or do you want to switch and do the borders?"
    hi "で、お前はこれをどう割り振りたいんだ？　お前が文字をやって、俺たちは縁をやるか？　それとも、お前が縁をやるか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3088
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_ebc9d1f4:

    # ke "Text is mine. You do borders."
    ke "文字は俺がやる。縁を頼む"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3090
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_c74a9142:

    # "He has surprisingly strong feelings on the topic."
    "こいつ、驚くほど気合いが入っているな。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3095
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_9923171c:

    # "As I reach over to grab a brush, I notice Hanako's already debating between colors to use."
    "俺がハケを取ろうと手を伸ばしたときには、華子はもう使う色で悩んでいる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3106
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_a187938f:

    # "By the time I've put brush to cloth, she's already started on a delicate pattern. Looks like my idea of taking her mind off everyone around her worked."
    "ハケを入れるころには、華子は細かい模様を描き始めていた。華子の気を逸らす、という俺の考えは成功したようだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3108
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_1ac6ef38:

    # "With a dark blue stroke, the three of us silently get to work."
    "紺色の線を描きながら、俺たち三人は黙々と作業を始める。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3110
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_cd99183a:

    # "Not before Kenji takes advantage of Hanako's working to lean towards me and whisper conspiratorially, though."
    "やがて、華子が作業中なのをいいことに、健二がこっちに体を寄せてなにやら耳打ちしてくる。おかげで俺の作業は邪魔されてしまう。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3124
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_4c71eee5:

    # ke "Okay man, why're you here?"
    ke "さて、何でここにいるんだ？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3126
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_6d0afe6b:

    # hi "Hanako just wanted some help to find Lilly, that's all."
    hi "華子がリリーを探すのを手伝ってほしいって、それだけさ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3131
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_e02fe49f:

    # "He apparently disapproves of my motivations."
    "健二はどうやら俺の動機に納得していないようだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3133
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_b125f211:

    # ke "I get it. It looks like I misjudged you."
    ke "なるほど。俺はお前を誤解してたようだ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3138
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_70300ab6:

    # ke "You're infiltrating them, aren't you? Going deep undercover?"
    ke "潜入捜査中ってわけだな？　組織の奥深くまで"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3140
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_0474b0a2:

    # "I should have guessed. Letting the truth slip by him would probably be better than outright lying or annoying him, in any case."
    "そうだよな。こいつに本当のことを教えるより、すぐばれるような嘘をついてやるか、ちょっと挑発してやったほうがましだっただろう。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3142
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_dfc13255:

    # hi "Is that why you're here?"
    hi "だからお前はここにいるのか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3144
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_ab215617:

    # ke "Obviously. It sucks, but there's no better way to get intel than going in yourself."
    ke "当然だ。かったるいけど、情報収集には自分で潜入するのが一番だからな"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3149
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_f53bd240:

    # ke "We gotta stick together, man. This is a harsh school, a harsh world."
    ke "離れるなよ。ここは過酷な学校、過酷な世界だ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3151
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_8a373c97:

    # hi "Yes, very harsh."
    hi "そうだな、とってもキツイよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3153
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_a718c6e3:

    # "He misses my true meaning as he leans back, satisfied I'm sympathetic to his cause. I'd better get down to work."
    "健二は俺の真意に気づかず、同意を得たことに満足して持ち場に戻る。作業に取り掛からないと。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3163
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_3031f728:

    # ha "Finished."
    ha "おわりました"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3165
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_0c0b3ca6:

    # hi "Looks like I am too. Good job."
    hi "俺も。お疲れさま"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3167
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_bdb11e90:

    # "The two of us connect up the lines of our patterns, mine being as close a copy as I could manage of hers."
    "二人の模様の線をつなぐ。俺の模様はできるだけ華子が描いたものを真似してある。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3172
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_97b3bdbd:

    # "With a grunt, I lever myself up from the floor and look around."
    "うめきながら腰を上げ、辺りを見回す。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3176
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_660166a1:

    # "Aside from Hanako and myself, there's only Kenji left finishing off a sign as well as Lilly and a couple of students talking among themselves in the classroom."
    "華子と俺以外に教室に残っているのは、垂れ幕を仕上げている健二に、話し合っているリリーと数名の生徒だけだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3178
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_3b82fa31:

    # "Looking at my watch, it's no surprise. It's getting pretty late."
    "腕時計を見て納得する。もうかなり遅い時間だ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3180
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_cde208c6:

    # hi "Need a hand?"
    hi "手を貸そうか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3188
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_14d7417f:

    # "I offer a hand to Hanako, which she uses to get herself up."
    "手を差し伸べると、華子は立ち上がろうと手をつかむ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3190
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_4e26b7b6:

    # "As she does, I can't help but glance at her wrist; if her scars extend even to there, just how much of her body was burned?"
    "そうすると、つい華子の手首に目がいってしまう。ここまでやけどが広がっているなら、華子の体は一体どこまで焼けてしまったんだろうか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3195
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_52d82ff5:

    # "I feel a pang of guilt about it however as she quickly covers her wrist with her other hand."
    "華子がもう一方の手で素早く手首を覆い隠すのを見て、罪悪感に襲われる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3197
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_f9092078:

    # hi "Looks good, doesn't it?"
    hi "なかなか綺麗じゃない？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3202
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_4706f473:

    # "She looks surprised for a moment before noticing that I mean the banner."
    "華子は驚いたようだったけど、俺が垂れ幕のことを言ったんだと気づく。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3207
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_43aca7bf:

    # ha "It does… I guess."
    ha "そう……かも、ですね"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3209
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_44770b9f:

    # "Her smile shows that she feels a slight sense of pride in the result, just as I do."
    "華子の笑顔からは、達成感がにじみ出ている。俺も同じだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3214
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_247a5861:

    # "With the floor significantly neater for the decorations being placed on desks and shelves, it's much easier to get to Lilly as we cross the room."
    "飾りつけは机や棚の上に置かれ、床の上は片付いている。おかげでさっきより楽にリリーの所に行くことができる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3216
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_f4d86cfa:

    # hi "We've finished the banner. I guess that's all that needs to be done?"
    hi "垂れ幕は終わったよ。これで全部？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3222
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_c4affa36:

    # "Lilly gives an appreciative nod."
    "リリーはうなずいて感謝の意を示す。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3227
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_52decb1c:

    # li "Thank you Hisao, Hanako. If there's any way I can thank you…?"
    li "ありがとう、久夫さん、華ちゃん。何かお礼にできることは……？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3229
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_8326490b:

    # hi "It's fine. Beats sitting in my room studying, at any rate."
    hi "別にいいよ。どっちみち、自分の部屋で勉強してるよりはマシだから"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3234
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_ab896f85:

    # ha "I don't mind either."
    ha "気にしなくていいよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3236
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_79e0d992:

    # "She nods, before suddenly remembering one last person."
    "リリーはうなずくと、最後の一人を思い出す。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3241
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_d3d10924:

    # li "Oh, is Kenji still here?"
    li "あ、瀬藤くんはまだここに？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3243
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_3d833b85:

    # "Just as I open my mouth, Kenji gives the answer from the other side of the room."
    "俺が答えようとした時、部屋の向こう側から健二が言葉を返す。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3245
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_6e74dc16:

    # ke "Yeah, just finished."
    ke "ああ、今終わったとこ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3247
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_d0a892ce:

    # "He carefully slides his sign onto an empty section of shelf to dry, before quickly walking past us and out the door."
    "ペンキを乾かすために、健二は垂れ幕を空いた場所にそっと滑らせて置き、そそくさと部屋を出ていく。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3258
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_6b771a12:

    # ke "Seeya man."
    ke "じゃーな"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3260
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_361fdc97:

    # hi "Bye."
    hi "おう"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3270
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_3f657a54:

    # "The remaining two students say their goodbyes to Lilly before taking their cue to leave as well, leaving only the three of us."
    "他に残っている学生２人がリリーにさよならを告げて出て行くと、俺たち３人だけになる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3272
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_f4188c4f:

    # hi "Well, I guess that's everyone."
    hi "さて、これで全員かな"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3277
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_4fbbbff1:

    # li "I hope we don't have to do anything like that again."
    li "もうこんなことはせずに済めばいいんですけど"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3279
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_bae22e91:

    # hi "Working past schooltime?"
    hi "放課後も作業するってこと？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3284
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_201f43f8:

    # li "Indeed. The class's plans this year were ambitious. Maybe too ambitious."
    li "そうです。今年のクラスの企画は意欲的でした。意欲的すぎたのかもしれません"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3289
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_c949d738:

    # ha "The stalls look nice, though."
    ha "でも、屋台は良く出来てるよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3291
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_837fabb2:

    # hi "She's right, it shows that a lot of work's gone into them."
    hi "華子の言う通りだよ。たくさん手がかかってるってことさ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3296
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_81475ff8:

    # li "My my, I'm sure a lot of us would be glad to hear that. At least now there's not much work to do until the festival itself."
    li "あらあら、それを聞いたらみなさん喜びますよ。あとはもう、学園祭までにする仕事は大してありませんから"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3301
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_ac5d4a55:

    # ha "Umm… It's getting pretty late. Should we go?"
    ha "ええと……かなり遅い時間だよ。もう行かない？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3306
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_83ce77d5:

    # li "That's probably a good idea. Are you going back to the dorms as well, Hisao?"
    li "それが良いですね。久夫さん、一緒に寮に戻ります？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3308
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_73a75d1e:

    # hi "Yeah, I guess I'll tag along."
    hi "そうだな、じゃあ一緒に行くよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3313
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_ce06ea1a:

    # "The nighttime lighting really makes the gardens look quite different. Compared to the usual look of lush greenery, things are much more calm."
    "夜の照明で、校庭がまったく違って見える。いつもの青々とした草木と比べて、いろいろなものが穏やかだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3315
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_01ce1095:

    # "Being that it's so late, the lack of students around probably helps. The odd one or two can be seen scurrying to and from the dorms trying to eke the most out of their approaching curfews, but no more."
    "時間が遅いのと、辺りに生徒がいないことが大きいんだろう。寮の門限までの時間を有効活用しようとする、急ぎ足の生徒が一人二人いるぐらいだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3317
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_5929c529:

    # "All that can be heard is our footsteps, in addition to Lilly's cane regularly gently tapping the ground in front of her."
    "聞こえるのは俺たちの足音と、前方の地面を叩く、リリーの白杖の規則的で緩やかな音だけ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3319
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_edb2703c:

    # "It's nice to finally be able to relax a bit after the mad rush during school."
    "学校での大変な慌しさの後で、ようやく落ち着くことができるのはうれしいものだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3321
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_8b061b92:

    # "Without even noticing it, I let out a small yawn."
    "俺は無意識に小さな欠伸を漏らす。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3327
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_df893cae:

    # li "Tired?"
    li "疲れました？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3329
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_4ad2d15a:

    # hi "Yeah. Still getting used to the flow of things, I guess."
    hi "まあね。それでもここの暮らしには慣れてきてると思うよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3331
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_f05c18cb:

    # hi "The… uh… thing… with Shizune took me kind of off guard, though."
    hi "あの……えーと、静音との件……あれはちょっと驚いたけどな"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3333
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_5b6150d5:

    # "I grit my teeth a little at the candid mention of their rather public spat. That said, I do want to sort out what in the world was behind it."
    "リリーたちの大っぴらな口げんかのことをずばり言ってしまい、歯を食いしばる。それでも、いったいどんな事情があったのかをはっきりさせたい。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3338
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_b34e9471:

    # li "Ah… about that…"
    li "あ……そのことは……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3340
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_ebb6d396:

    # li "I'm sorry about it being so public. Shizune and I… go back some ways."
    li "あんな人目につく所でごめんなさい。羽加道さんと私とは……以前からこうなんです"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3342
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_74d58c90:

    # "Her voice seems slightly irritated as she remembers Shizune, obviously unwilling to discuss it any further."
    "静音のことを思い出して、リリーの声がわずかに苛立つ。明らかに、これ以上話したくないらしい。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3347
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_369ff764:

    # "I glance to Hanako for her views on this, but her expression is, unsurprisingly, evasive and difficult to read."
    "意見を求めて華子をちらりと見る。でも、その表情はいつも通りつかみどころがなく、読むのが難しい。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3349
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_487ce202:

    # "Either way I guess her apologizing for it is something, even if my curiosity goes unanswered."
    "何にしたって、リリーが口げんかについて謝ったのは大したものだと思う。事情はわからないままだけど。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3354
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_837783be:

    # li "I'll be glad once the festival is over, in any case."
    li "ともかく、学園祭が過ぎてしまえば良いですね"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3356
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_5e4150c5:

    # "The change of topic's welcome, clearing the thickening air quickly."
    "話題が変わるのはありがたい。重たい雰囲気がさっと吹き飛ぶ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3358
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_e24350b5:

    # hi "I can imagine. My old school's festivals were a lot more low-key than this."
    hi "気持ちはわかるよ。前の学校の文化祭はこれよりもっとおとなしかったから"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3363
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_8a695294:

    # li "Yamaku stresses the idea of a school community, so the staff likes to make our festivals and such special occasions."
    li "山久学園は学校社会という理想を重視します。それで職員方は文化祭や特別なイベントを行うのが好きなんですよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3365
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_7f85d0b3:

    # hi "And yet the students are the ones who do the work. What an unfair world."
    hi "それなのに作業をしてるのは生徒じゃないか。世の中不公平だな"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3371
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_b25243f8:

    # "Hanako and Lilly both chuckle in agreement, savoring the fact that none of the staff are around to hear our grumbling."
    "華子とリリーは同意してクスクス笑う。職員が周りにいないから、俺たちの文句が聞かれないこの状況をありがたく思う。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3377
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_f258d5cf:

    # li "I suppose coming from a strict all-girls school helped me a bit with Yamaku. Compared to there, Yamaku is much more relaxed."
    li "私は厳格な女子校から転校してきたので、それがここで役に立っているのだと思います。そこに比べれば、山久はずっとゆったりしてますしね"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3379
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_5d2503c8:

    # "That'd go a way towards explaining her well-bred speech and behavior, in any case."
    "なら、それでリリーは上品な話し方と物腰になったんだろう。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3386
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_f256150c:

    # "As we come up to the dormitories, it eventually comes time to leave for our respective rooms."
    "寮に着き、それぞれの部屋へと別れる時がくる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3388
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_dbd341e5:

    # hi "See you Lilly, Hanako."
    hi "じゃあな、リリー、華子"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3390
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_b65063e4:

    # "The two both give polite nods before setting off to the women's dorms, just next to the guys'."
    "二人は礼儀正しくお辞儀をして、男子寮のすぐ隣にある女子寮に向かう。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3398
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_84ee7db3:

    # "As is to be expected of such an arrangement, there's a staff member casually patrolling around outside to prevent any nighttime shenanigans."
    "夜間のいたずらを防ぐために、職員がさりげなく建物の外を見回っている。まあ、それは予想通りだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3400
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_f467fabc:

    # "Walking past him, I quickly stretch my arms and rub my neck, both quite sore after having worked on the floor for so long, before walking to my room."
    "職員の横を通り、自分の部屋まで歩きながら、ぐっと腕を伸ばし、首をさする。ずっと床で作業していたから、どっちもズキズキする。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3402
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_afad8002:

    # "It feels good to actually have direction, though. After so long in the hospital, the everyday facts of studying, homework and teachers seem almost a blessing."
    "だけど実際、やることがあるのは気分が良い。病院で長い間過ごした後では、勉強に宿題、先生たちという日常の出来事も天の恵みとすら思える。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3404
translate jp a1_thursday_paint_by_numbers_d239112b:

    # "I guess if things continue like this, my time at Yamaku might turn out okay."
    "こんな日々が続くなら、山久での暮らしはうまくいくかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3424
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_08c41f2f:

    # "Hanako nods quickly and retreats with haste."
    "華子はすばやくうなずき、早足で出て行く。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3431
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_d9569cc8:

    # mi "What were we talking about? Oh yeah, we are really working hard to make the festival happen."
    mi "なんの話だったっけ？　そうだ、学園祭の成功に向けて、わたしたちすごくがんばってるわけなんだよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3433
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_02cc1c2d:

    # "And driving other people insane along the way."
    "そのために他人をあんなふうに責め立てるって言うのか。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3435
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_15f90e3f:

    # hi "Well, good luck with that."
    hi "そうかい、まあせいぜい頑張ってくれよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3437
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_4a0f79ee:

    # "I stand up to leave, making my exit before either of them manages to berate me any more for slacking off."
    "俺は立ち上がり、二人にこれ以上だらけた態度を叱責される前に教室を出る。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3442
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_0f0447b9:

    # "The halls are somewhat quiet, as expected. Everyone must be in club meetings or at festival preparations. Or both."
    "ホールは予想通り少しは静かだ。皆、部活や学園祭の準備に取り掛かっているんだろう。あるいはその両方で。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3444
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_fe341652:

    # "Shizune's words about being a slacker echo in my head."
    "俺が怠けているという静音の言葉がぼんやりと頭の中に反響する。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3446
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_da2ace70:

    # "I feel a bit guilty about not contributing, but I seem to lack the resolve to do something concrete about the matter."
    "準備を手伝わないことに悪い気がしてくる。だけど俺は具体的に何かしようという意欲が欠けているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3448
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_9060482e:

    # "For the festival, it's too late already unless I count helping Shizune and Misha which I naturally don't. And clubs… I don't know."
    "学園祭については、もう遅いだろう。静音とミーシャをアテにすれば別だけど、もちろん頼る気はない。部活は……いや、わからないな。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3450
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_03046b73:

    # "Maybe I'm not a club type of a person."
    "俺は部活に意気込むような人間ではないのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3457
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_1d33f012:

    # "Halfway through the way from the school building to the dorms I spot a figure in front of the dorms."
    "校舎から寮までの道を半分ほど進んだところで、俺は寮の前に人影を見つける。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3459
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_e81120f5:

    # "It's Rin."
    "琳だ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3461
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_1c1af2a1:

    # "It looks like she is working on her mural today too."
    "今日も琳は壁画に向かっているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3463
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_0a8855e8:

    # "I walk over to her, but she doesn't seem to notice me approaching."
    "俺は琳に歩み寄るが、向こうは俺が近づいてくるのに気づいていないようだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3469
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_6c50dc42:

    # "She's sitting on an upturned box, looking intently at the wall she is painting with a brush held between her toes."
    "琳はひっくり返した箱の上に座り、熱心につま先のブラシで描いた絵を眺めている。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3471
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_71b259dd:

    # "The mural has progressed considerably since yesterday but it's still only half-done as far as I can tell."
    "壁画は昨日から大分進展したようだった。しかし、俺が見る限りではまだ半分程度といったところだろう。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3473
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_14c9fe49:

    # "More colors have appeared and the twisted human-like figures have spread and increased in number."
    "より多彩な着色がされたようだ。そして捻れた人のような絵も色がつけられ、数も増えていた。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3475
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_0165c374:

    # "I have to say, the style is quite eye-catching and very unique. Not that I would be knowledgeable about art by any measurable scale, but it's very nice-looking, nevertheless."
    "実に印象的かつ独創的だ、と言わざるを得ない。どんな基準で見ても俺は芸術には詳しくない。けど、それでもこの絵は素晴らしいものに見える。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3477
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_f1e133e4:

    # "I clear my throat to get her attention, but not startle her so that her concentration won't break."
    "俺は琳を驚かせて集中を途切れさせてしまわないよう、咳払いをして注意を引く。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3479
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_286b119b:

    # rin "Wait."
    rin "待って"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3481
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_9526d632:

    # "She doesn't even turn to check who it is."
    "琳は相手が誰なのか確かめようともしない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3483
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_36bc5377:

    # "I'll wait."
    "しかし、ここは待とう。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3487
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3489
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3491
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_ce617998_2:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3493
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_ce617998_3:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3497
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_ce617998_4:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3499
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_992aa90c:

    # "Fifteen minutes later I decide that her concentration is indeed unbroken, and also that I have waited long enough to warrant poking her gently on the shoulder to remind her of my presence."
    "１５分ほどしても、琳の集中は途切れていないようだ。もう十分長い間待ったし、琳の肩を叩いて注意を引くことにする。そのくらいはしてもいいだろう。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3501
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_325e76c3:

    # "Rin turns her head mechanically to my direction, ending up staring at my crotch level."
    "琳は俺の方にぎこちなく頭を向けると、股の高さで目を止める。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3506
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_51f140c5:

    # rin "Oh, it's Hisao."
    rin "ああ、久夫"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3510
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_ce228208:

    # "She can tell? I would feel a lot less uncomfortable if she would look at my face."
    "わかったのか？　顔を見て言ってくれれば良かったんだけど……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3512
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_c54bbb24:

    # hi "An astute observation. Hard at work, I see."
    hi "よくわかったな……大変そうだな"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3514
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_9a3f9c8b:

    # "The conversation starts as if I hadn't been here for a quarter of an hour already, but it's not a concern. At least it starts."
    "１５分前からいたのがなかったことのように会話が始まる。でもそんなことはいい。少なくとも話が始まったんだから。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3516
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_7ef3c856:

    # hi "Looking good."
    hi "よく描けてるな"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3518
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_6900d4b7:

    # "It does, the layers of paint hiding other layers of paint, mixing and shaping the human figures really create an impressive look. But Rin looks miffed."
    "それは確かだ。ペンキの層が重なり合い、並び合い、実に印象的なヒトの形を作り出す。しかし琳はムッとした表情になる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3523
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_4fdd8137:

    # rin "You shouldn't comment on works in progress. Seven years of bad luck."
    rin "描いてる途中の絵に口出ししちゃダメ。７年間不幸になるんだよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3525
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_12830e16:

    # hi "Sounds terrible. I guess I'll take it back then."
    hi "そりゃおっかない。じゃあ今のは取り消すよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3527
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_870acfd8:

    # "Still, it looks good. I wonder if I get fourteen years of bad luck for thinking that."
    "それでも、やはりいい絵に見える。果たしてそう考えたら１４年間不幸になるんだろうか、と疑問に思う。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3532
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_78c6250d:

    # "Rin turns back to look at her painting and pokes it with a big toe."
    "琳は壁に向き直ると、足の親指で絵を小突く。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3537
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_0b5432f4:

    # rin "Could you mix some of this color? I am running out of it."
    rin "ペンキ、混ぜてくれる？　もう使い切っちゃいそうなんだ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3539
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_378e9cf1:

    # "She looks down at a half-empty bowl with the remains of the same pinkish paint in it."
    "琳はピンクっぽいペンキが半分ほど残ったボウルを覗き込む。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3541
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_f25c36d7:

    # "I didn't really intend to stay and help her with this project though… I guess I didn't intend to do anything much."
    "俺はここに残って、琳の企画を手伝うつもりなどなかったのだけど……というよりも、何をするつもりでもなかった。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3546
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_32d2f295:

    # "I look at Rin, she looks emptily back at me."
    "俺は琳を見やる。彼女も俺をぼんやりと見る。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3548
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_276c3b32:

    # hi "Just this once."
    hi "じゃあ、今回だけな"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3553
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_74d45232:

    # "Rin picks up another brush and drenches it in another tone of pale red. There are dozens of similar bowls all around her working area. From the looks of this scene she could have been sitting there for hours."
    "琳は別のブラシを拾い上げ、淡い赤のペンキに浸す。何十もの似たようなボウルが琳を取り囲んでいる。それを見る限り、琳はここに何時間も座っていたのだろう。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3555
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_9f642639:

    # "I wonder if she has. That would mean she'd have been skipping school though, which I of course wouldn't put beyond someone like Rin."
    "ふと不思議に思う。つまりそれは琳が授業をサボっているということになるが、まあ琳ならやりかねないだろう。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3557
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_9043af75:

    # "I pour a little bit of white and red into the bowl, trying to match the color with the one already on the wall."
    "俺は少量の赤と白のペンキをボウルに流し込み、壁に塗られたものに合わせようとする。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3559
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_5bbc81b9:

    # "I can't seem to get it right."
    "どうも上手くいかない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3561
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_4702c8fa:

    # "It's really inconvenient of her to not mix enough in the first place. Getting it to be exactly the same tone will be impossible, but at least I can try to get as close as I can."
    "そもそも琳が前もって十分な量のペンキを混ぜておいてくれれば、こんな面倒なことにはならなかったのに。しかしまったく同じ色を作るのは不可能でも、できるだけ近い色にすることくらいはできる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3563
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_bd77247d:

    # hi "Speaking of hard work, isn't that a huge workload for you too? It's such a big painting and all."
    hi "ちょっと訊くけど、こんなに大きい絵だと一人じゃやりきれないんじゃないのか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3568
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_810ebb92:

    # rin "Oh, I’m not old and bitter enough yet to think like that."
    rin "まあ、私はまだそんな風に考え出すほど歳でもなければ偏屈でもないから"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3570
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_90d6bc56:

    # hi "I guess you aren't."
    hi "まあそうなんだろうな"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3575
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_08a5da89:

    # rin "You guessed right."
    rin "そういうこと"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3580
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_f5e6680c:

    # rin "Legs hurt though. They feel like slugs. Slugs made of sea slugs."
    rin "足は痛むけどね。ナメクジみたいな感じがする。ナマコで作ったナメクジみたいなさ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3582
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_28dc56e2:

    # hi "Because of the position?"
    hi "その姿勢のせいか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3584
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_f1b1c5c7:

    # rin "Yeah, I like doing it in a horizontal position more, if you know what I'm talking about."
    rin "うん。もっと体を横にしてやりたいな。言ってることわかる？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3586
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_da4361c6:

    # rin "But it can't be helped. Can't ask the wall to lay down."
    rin "ま、でも仕方ないよね。壁にむかって『横になってくれ』なんて言えないし"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3591
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_f822e2ea:

    # "Saying that, she stretches herself a little, bending her legs and back far more than a human should flex. It's astonishing how effortlessly she manages her body around."
    "そう言うと、琳は体を伸ばす。足と背中が普通の人間よりもはるかに大きく曲がる。琳の軽々とした身のこなしに驚かされる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3599
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_c4ede0d0:

    # "There is a small flinch in her otherwise blank expression - a hint of pain maybe - as she stretches out her calves."
    "ふくらはぎを伸ばしていると、琳の普段ならうつろな顔に、少しだけひるむような――少し痛んだのだろうか――表情が浮かぶ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3601
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_7497cc9e:

    # "Rin must have stamina and dexterity far above a normal person to be able to live like she does, but she's wearing out working on this."
    "琳には生活していくために、常人をはるかに超えたスタミナと器用さがあるに違いない。それでもこの壁画の作業で疲れが溜まっているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3603
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_f62239b3:

    # hi "Why push yourself so much? Take a break or something at least. Continue tomorrow if it's bad."
    hi "どうしてそんなに無理するんだ？　少し休憩するとかしろよ。疲れてるなら明日また続ければいいじゃないか"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3608
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_46918c68:

    # "This gives her a pause."
    "その言葉に琳は動きを止める。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3610
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_52749036:

    # "A long one too, feeling like a mental yawn."
    "しかも長い間。心の中であくびをしているような感じだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3612
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_ce617998_5:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3617
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_f1def3e8:

    # rin "I don't think so, Hisao."
    rin "私はそうは思わないな、久夫"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3619
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_eea71d70:

    # rin "I'm not pushing myself."
    rin "別に無理なんかしてないよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3621
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_3d51bfae:

    # hi "Sure looks like you are."
    hi "……でも、大分無理してるように見えるぞ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3626
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_80cf350d:

    # rin "No. It's not about pushing or pulling or anything related to that kind of thing."
    rin "いや、無理するしないとか、そういう話じゃないんだよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3631
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_c1c94784:

    # rin "There is this boy."
    rin "男の子がいるんだ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3633
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_e64aba46:

    # hi "A boy?"
    hi "男の子？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3638
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_33e2e19e:

    # rin "Yes."
    rin "うん"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3640
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_804bb8e8:

    # hi "Where?"
    hi "どこに？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3645
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_aecea18b:

    # rin "At the art club."
    rin "美術部に"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3647
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_1df4b68a:

    # hi "Err… and?"
    hi "ああ……はいはい。それで？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3652
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_e016f51c:

    # rin "He is blind."
    rin "その子、盲目なんだ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3654
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_f4deb3d7:

    # hi "Oh. How can you paint if you are blind?"
    hi "あぁ……目が見えなかったら、どうやって絵を描くんだ？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3659
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_c7cccc3e:

    # rin "No idea."
    rin "さぁね"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3661
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_123a7e6f:

    # hi "So why is he there?"
    hi "それで、何でそいつは美術部に？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3666
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_330caf6c:

    # rin "That's the point. He is there."
    rin "そこがミソ。目の見えない彼は美術部にいる"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3668
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_87798c01:

    # "She really should speak more than one word at a time to make this feel more like a discussion and less like an interrogation."
    "そんな一言ずつじゃなくて、もっとまとめてしゃべってくれればいいのに。これじゃ会話じゃなくて尋問みたいだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3673
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_2e3f027a:

    # rin "He can't really do anything that you'd call art, right? But he comes there anyway. And paints."
    rin "その子は芸術と呼べるようなことは何も出来ない、いい？　それでも彼はやって来て、絵を描いてる"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3678
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_d66e33b2:

    # rin "Why?"
    rin "どーしてだ？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3680
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_3ff9fda1:

    # hi "I don't know. Why?"
    hi "さぁ、わからない。どうしてだ？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3685
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_dd4a8406:

    # rin "I don't know. That's why I asked."
    rin "私もわからない。だから訊いたんだよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3687
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_d5bdc909:

    # hi "So?"
    hi "……それで？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3692
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_e84f2113:

    # rin "He doesn't paint often but I think his paintings are very interesting."
    rin "そう頻繁に描くわけじゃないけど、でも彼の描く絵ってすごい面白いんだよね"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3694
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_b605045b:

    # hi "I'm sure they are."
    hi "ああ、きっとそうなんだろうな"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3699
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_8b43f78f:

    # rin "I once tried that. Painting with eyes closed."
    rin "私も１回やってみたんだ。目、つむって"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3704
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_3a71f462:

    # rin "Wasn't too interesting. And cleaning up the floor took ages. Didn't try again."
    rin "でもつまんなかった。床をきれいにするのに苦労したし。それからもうやってない"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3709
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_02725c33:

    # rin "But he is becoming better at sculpting."
    rin "でもその子、彫刻は上手くなってるんだ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3711
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_e1f8a5e6:

    # hi "I see."
    hi "へぇ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3713
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_8d6aa3b3:

    # "Maybe she was trying to make a point with this. Maybe she forgot she had one."
    "琳はこの話を通して何か言いたいことがあったのかもしれない。だけどその言いたいことを忘れてしまったのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3715
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_5e093482:

    # hi "Seems like the art club is full of interesting people."
    hi "美術部ってのは面白いヤツがいっぱいいるんだな"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3720
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_4d44250e:

    # rin "Not really."
    rin "そうでもないよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3722
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_88020a8b:

    # "Pretty blunt statement, and she totally missed the sarcasm."
    "何だかぶっきらぼうに言うが、皮肉めいた感じはまったくしない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3724
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_981ecd03:

    # hi "No?"
    hi "違うのか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3729
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_8ca59def:

    # rin "Just like I said. They are not very interesting. I usually don't have much interest in people who are not interesting."
    rin "違うんだよ。別に面白い人たちじゃないの。普通、私は面白くもない人にはたいして興味湧かないよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3734
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_50c69259:

    # rin "Maybe you have."
    rin "君は湧くのかもしれないけど"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3736
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_da9749d8:

    # hi "Maybe."
    hi "そうかもな"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3738
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_ce617998_6:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3743
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_baa7c3db:

    # rin "But that boy is interesting."
    rin "でも、その子は面白いの"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3748
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_fc5f4e3f:

    # rin "Maybe I am like that boy, or maybe you are. Maybe everyone is."
    rin "たぶん私はあの子に似てるんじゃないかな？　あるいはキミが似てるのかも。ひょっとしたら皆似てるのかも"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3750
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_3f84a51f:

    # rin "Doing things you can't do, just because you can."
    rin "出来ないことをやろうとするのは、それが本当は出来るからなんだよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3752
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_900b7e04:

    # "That's pretty deep I think, and tell that to her."
    "奥の深い話だな、と思う。そしてそれを琳に伝える。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3754
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_32bcf8fb:

    # hi "You're a deep one."
    hi "お前も奥の深いヤツだな"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3759
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_6a507826:

    # rin "Nah. I'm a really shallow and thoughtless person. People say that to me all the time."
    rin "んーん。私なんて浅い、いっつも考えの足りない人間だよ。皆そう言うんだけどなぁ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3764
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_59f5fc89:

    # rin "Did you know I can only think of four things at the same time?"
    rin "私って一度に４つのことしか考えられないんだ。知ってた？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3766
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_0b8d2c63:

    # hi "No, but now I do."
    hi "……いや、今知ったよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3771
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_ce42a143:

    # rin "Right now I'm thinking of the second floor's girls' toilet, ice-cream-flavored ice cream, the middle toe, and a haircut."
    rin "で、今は２階の女子トイレ、アイス味のアイスクリーム、足の中指、あと髪を切ることを考えてるってわけ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3776
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_0cbfb799:

    # rin "I'm going to need a haircut."
    rin "そろそろ髪、切りに行かないとね"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3802
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_73ced15e:

    # "She shakes her head around vigorously, letting her short and messy hair ruffle wildly around. I can see that doing it is something she likes to do."
    "琳は景気良く頭を振って、乱れた髪を逆立たせて見せる。その仕草は琳も気に入っているようだった。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3807
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_78186863:

    # "We fall silent as Rin treads around absentmindedly, poking some brushes around. The thought about the art club sticks in my head for a while longer."
    "俺たちが沈黙に陥ると、琳はそこらをぼんやりと歩き始め、時折ブラシを突きまわしていく。俺はもうしばらく美術部のことを考えていた。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3809
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_15551bce:

    # "I'm feeling like I'm treading on very unknown territory with art. The way these meetings with Rin go, it's as though I'm starting a smoking habit or something. I should probably stop talking with her."
    "俺は芸術について、未知の領域にまで足を踏み入れつつあるような気がする。琳と会っているときの俺の様子ときたら、まるで煙草でも吸い始めた未成年みたいだ。 だとしたら、琳と話すのはもうやめたほうがいいってことになるかもしれないけど。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3811
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_6620fc6d:

    # "It’s not like I dislike her, despite the confusion her being herself causes, and I don't dislike art either. I’ve even drawn for fun sometimes. I just don’t have a real creative drive, or any technical skill."
    "琳の存在自体は何かと混乱のもとだけど、俺は琳のことも芸術も嫌いじゃない。暇つぶしに絵を描いたことだってある。ただ俺にはそれ以上の創作意欲や技術がないだけだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3813
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_25f143be:

    # "So usually, if I were to draw something, I get white paper syndrome and just freeze completely."
    "それで、何か絵に描こうとすると『白紙症候群』にかかって、何も出来なくなってしまう。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3815
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_bcf04375:

    # "That, or I manage to draw something disfigured and promptly get frustrated at my inability to put the picture in my head down on the paper, then call it quits without really even trying to make an effort."
    "あるいはなんとかヘタクソな絵を描き上げては、頭の中のイメージを紙に描きだせない、自分の能力のなさに必然的にイラついて、それ以上努力もせずに諦めてしまうか。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3817
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_e017be35:

    # "Rin clearly doesn't have this problem… but she frustrates me in another way. Being with her is like looking into a mirror that doesn't reflect anything."
    "琳にはどう見てもそんな問題はない……でも琳は別の意味で俺を苛立たせる。琳と一緒にいると、何も映らない鏡を見ているような気分になる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3819
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_8bfef70c:

    # "It makes one question the sanity of the act."
    "そんなことをしていると、自分の正気を疑いたくなる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3824
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_6cb359c8:

    # "Rin sits down on her box, swaying from side to side, apparently comfortable with the uncomfortable silence. She is staring at me again, or maybe over my shoulder. I can’t quite figure out where her eyes are focused."
    "琳は箱に座り、右に左に体を揺らす。この落ち着かない沈黙が落ち着くようだ。そして再び俺を見すえる。あるいは俺の肩の向こう側を。どこに焦点を合わせているのか、まるでわからない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3826
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_6d44ca17:

    # "I'm thinking of leaving so she can carry on working undistracted and that I can do whatever I'm going to do alone. It's not like I have anything that must be done today…"
    "そろそろこの場を離れようと思う。そうすれば琳は気を散らさずに作業を進められるし、俺も一人でやりたいことが出来る。もっとも、俺は今日はやることはないが……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3828
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_d8043cab:

    # hi "Oh, shoot."
    hi "あ、しまった"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3833
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_318a511c:

    # rin "Who?"
    rin "何が？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3835
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_b4713998:

    # hi "Nobody, I just forgot to tell Hanako that Lilly was looking for her."
    hi "いや何も。華子にリリーが探してたって伝えるのを忘れてたんだ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3837
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_a72bd963:

    # hi "Do you know her? From my class?"
    hi "知ってるか？　俺のクラスの……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3842
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_bc292fe2:

    # rin "Oh, her. The Mystery Toilet Girl."
    rin "ああ、あの子ね。『謎のトイレ少女』"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3847
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_05053f93:

    # rin "That person is funny. I saw her going to the toilet five times during one recess three weeks ago. I'm sure it's the world record."
    rin "面白い人だよね。３週間前、１回の休みの間に５回もトイレに行ってたんだよ。間違いなく世界記録"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3852
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_1c975ab3:

    # rin "It was very mysterious."
    rin "すごい謎だよね"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3854
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_77a3b840:

    # hi "That's why you call her Mystery Toilet Girl?"
    hi "それで『トイレ少女』なんて呼んでるのか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3859
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_c9e4664f:

    # rin "What other reason could there possibly be? Well, if there is, it's an eternal mystery. I didn't follow her in there."
    rin "他にどんな理由があるってのさ。あったとしても、永遠に謎だよ。トイレの中まではついていかなかったから"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3861
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_ce617998_7:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3866
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_4a9c521f:

    # rin "Maybe it was the week before that? Could have been."
    rin "それともその前の週だったかなあ？　確かそうだったかも"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3868
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_ce617998_8:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3870
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_00f5e742:

    # rin "Looking at her makes me hungry."
    rin "あの子を見てるとお腹が減るんだよね"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3872
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_9625677f:

    # hi "Don't say that."
    hi "そういうことは言うなよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3874
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_cc2b10dc:

    # hi "At least, not around her."
    hi "……少なくとも、本人の前では"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3879
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_db9a0c42:

    # "Rin turns to look at me blankly, as if she's not sure why I reproved her."
    "琳は振り返って俺をぼんやりと見る。俺がなぜとがめたのか、わかってないみたいだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3881
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_0f719e2c:

    # "But she doesn't acknowledge understanding any more than before, so I give up at this point."
    "しかし琳はそれ以上ちゃんと理解する様子を見せないので、俺はこの話を諦める。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3883
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_c635c66c:

    # hi "So do you want to go eat dinner then?"
    hi "それじゃあ、夕飯でも食べに行くか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3888
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_0dc020b2:

    # rin "No. Not yet."
    rin "ううん、まだいい"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3890
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_34ab3bb9:

    # "Rin has turned her hungry gaze back to the wall, looking slightly more energetic, or at least slightly less lethargic than she did before."
    "琳は空腹そうな視線を壁に向け直す。少しばかり気力が戻ったように見える。少なくとも、さっきまでの無気力さは少しだけ薄れている。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3892
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_e45c8a8e:

    # "It's as if the wall is an opponent she has to vanquish, something she must overcome before she can indulge in dinner."
    "まるでその壁が、琳が夕飯にありつく前に打ち破らなければならないもののようだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3894
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_03cf74e5:

    # "This is the feeling I get. A weird sense of empathy overcomes me and makes me smile a little to myself."
    "俺はそう感じる。琳への妙な共感が俺の中に生まれて、一人で小さく笑う。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3896
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_877602f9:

    # "For all her oddity, Rin is pretty cool after all."
    "色々とおかしなところはあるけど、やはり琳はすごいやつだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3898
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_083bd5f0:

    # hi "I'll be going anyway."
    hi "俺は行かなくちゃ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3900
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_5cdcc2d2:

    # hi "Have fun."
    hi "ごゆっくり"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3904
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_5c1c0ec5:

    # "Rin has already grasped a brush and is dipping it into fresh paint, so of course she can't hear me any more or doesn't answer anything even if she does."
    "琳はすでにブラシを新しいペンキに浸し始めている。当然俺の声は聞こえていないか、聞こえていたとしても返事をするつもりはないだろう。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3913
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_5abaf868:

    # "Adhering to the nurse's nagging voice in the back of my head, I set my alarm clock to wake me up early enough to go jogging again."
    "頭の隅に残るナースの小言を守り、目覚まし時計をセットする。早起きして、またジョギングに行けるように。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3915
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_6a14837d:

    # "I made a promise and I'm going to keep it. Besides, Emi is bound to rat on me if I don't show up."
    "約束したからには、ちゃんと守ってみせる。それに、行かなかったら笑美にチクられるに決まってる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3917
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_c02cd3b6:

    # "But it's not all that bad."
    "だけど、それもそんなに悪くないな。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3919
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_05cbd500:

    # "I'm feeling tired so I set my alarm clock to wake me up as late as I can afford, while still making it to the first class."
    "疲れた。ぎりぎりまで寝ていられるように目覚まし時計をセットする。一時間目に間に合えばいい。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3921
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_854419fc:

    # "The nurse's voice is almost nagging in the back of my head about morning jogs. I make a resolution to make up for it by going for a walk after school tomorrow."
    "頭の隅で、早朝ジョギングについてのナースの言葉がしつこく響く。明日の放課後散歩に行って、埋め合わせをすればいいさ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3923
translate jp a1_thursday_things_you_can_do_808044b4:

    # "Emi won't care either way, I bet."
    "どうせ笑美は気にもかけないさ。賭けてもいい。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3931
translate jp a1c8o1_20d1af17:

    # hi "Why am I being dragged into this, again? I've done more than enough, I think."
    hi "なんでまたこんな事に巻き込まれるんだ？　俺は十分やったと思うぞ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3933
translate jp a1c8o1_7c3f5e78:

    # hi "If you're angry with Lilly, that has nothing to do with me."
    hi "リリーに怒ってるんだったら、俺には関係ないだろ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3938
translate jp a1c8o1_9ab0ef04:

    # li "Now, wait just a second… are you implying the president is more right in scolding me than yourself?"
    li "あの、ちょっと待ってください……生徒会長が私を叱責するのは良くて、自分に矛先が向かうのはおかしいとでも言うんですか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3940
translate jp a1c8o1_ac541b1b:

    # "Ah damn, I think I could've worded that better."
    "しまった、今の言い方はまずかった。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3942
translate jp a1c8o1_b575f819:

    # hi "No, I don't know about that but… I mean…"
    hi "いや、そうじゃなくてさ、ほら……ええっと、つまり……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3947
translate jp a1c8o1_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3952
translate jp a1c8o1_a290cfee:

    # mi "What are you saying, Hicchan?"
    mi "何を言ってるの、ひっちゃん？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3954
translate jp a1c8o1_fd52e8aa:

    # hi "It's just that I hardly think it's fair you can say that, seeing that I've helped you guys."
    hi "お前のその言い方はフェアだと思えないってだけさ。俺だってお前達に協力したんだから"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3956
translate jp a1c8o1_81a64bb3:

    # "The mood has changed. This is like a showdown between two gunfighters now. Well, it was like that before too, but this time Shizune's focus is on me."
    "雰囲気が変わった。ガンマン同士の決闘みたいだ。まあ、さっきからそんな感じだけど。でも、今の静音の標的は俺だ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3958
translate jp a1c8o1_4da75675:

    # "And so is Lilly's, though she keeps quiet. I'm afraid I inadvertently pissed her off."
    "それに、黙ってはいるけど、リリーの標的も変わった。そんなつもりじゃなかったのに、リリーを怒らせてしまったようだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3963
translate jp a1c8o1_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3968
translate jp a1c8o1_4feb7fa5:

    # mi "Are you saying I'm wrong?"
    mi "わたしが間違ってるっていうの？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3970
translate jp a1c8o1_00492e72:

    # "What a dangerous situation."
    "一触即発だな。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3972
translate jp a1c8o1_c8549f3d:

    # hi "It's too early to argue with you. …Yes, I think it's unfair of you to get on my case."
    hi "お前と言い合うにはまだ早いよ……そうだ、お前が俺を責めるのはフェアじゃないと思う"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3977
translate jp a1c8o1_ef2b123c_2:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3982
translate jp a1c8o1_1050d892:

    # mi "Hicchan, you want too much~! But~! You have a point. Okay, okay okay~! You're not lazy, Hicchan."
    mi "ひっちゃんは欲張りすぎ～！　でも～！　それももっともだね。おっけー、おっけおっけ～！　ひっちゃんはさぼってないね"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3987
translate jp a1c8o1_66b999fb:

    # mi "Hahaha~!"
    mi "ははは～！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3989
translate jp a1c8o1_84dc3ce8:

    # "Shizune pushes her glasses up with her thumb, almost approvingly."
    "静音は満足そうにメガネを親指で押し上げる。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3994
translate jp a1c8o1_ef2b123c_3:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:3999
translate jp a1c8o1_ee04465d:

    # mi "That's good! If you're not useless, you shouldn't let anyone say you are~! But the next time I say it, it'll really be because you are disappointing me like Miss Class Rep here, so don't let this go to your head!"
    mi "よろしい！　自分が役立たずじゃないなら、他の人にもそんなことを言わせちゃだめ～！ でも次にわたしがそう言うときは、ひっちゃんがわたしの期待を裏切ったってことだからね。この学級委員さんみたいに。だからあんまり調子に乗らないようにね！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4004
translate jp a1c8o1_e0f50aa5:

    # "Lilly takes the jab silently, a venomous visage frozen on her face."
    "リリーは敵意に満ちた顔つきを崩さず、黙って静音の皮肉に耐える。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4009
translate jp a1c8o1_0f37ba22:

    # mi "Class rep~! Shicchan says: 'Don't forget that report, please~!'"
    mi "学級委員～！　しっちゃんが『申請書は忘れないでください』だって～！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4011
translate jp a1c8o1_220f407b:

    # li "I won't."
    li "忘れませんよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4016
translate jp a1c8o1_dacc2d09:

    # li "Would that be all?"
    li "お話はこれで終わりですか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4021
translate jp a1c8o1_f7267e24:

    # mi "Yup~!"
    mi "は～い！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4023
translate jp a1c8o1_d6257f93:

    # li "Then, good day to you all."
    li "ではごきげんよう、みなさん"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4025
translate jp a1c8o1_37e4bbcb:

    # "Her voice would cut the air of the classroom into half, if it was more tangible."
    "もしリリーの声が刃物だったら、教室の空気は真っ二つになっていただろう。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4030
translate jp a1c8o1_d49d3106:

    # "Lilly leaves the room, understandably in a bad mood but still managing to be as poised and calm as usual."
    "リリーが不機嫌なのも無理はない。それでも、いつも通りの落ち着きと穏やかさを保ったまま教室を出ていく。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4037
translate jp a1c8o1_2fee95e9:

    # hi "Shizune, you really did go a little too far today."
    hi "静音、今日はちょっとやりすぎだぞ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4042
translate jp a1c8o1_8b7e37c1:

    # mi "It's true, Shicchan, just a little~."
    mi "そうだよ、しっちゃん。ちょっとだけ～"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4044
translate jp a1c8o1_95db9639:

    # "If I had been expecting Shizune to grudgingly admit I have a point there as well, I think I was expecting too much. She doesn't respond."
    "俺の言い分をいやいやでも認めるんじゃないかと期待していたけど、甘かったようだ。静音は答えない。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4049
translate jp a1c8o1_ef2b123c_4:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4054
translate jp a1c8o1_65c18e5b:

    # mi "Hahaha~! Shicchan thinks you should mind your own business."
    mi "ははは～！　しっちゃんは余計なお世話だって言ってるよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4059
translate jp a1c8o1_bf4cdada:

    # mi "Hicchan, we have a few last minute things to take care of before class~! We might be late, so~! Can you please cover for us?"
    mi "ひっちゃん、授業の前にわたしたちやらなきゃいけないことがあるの～！　遅れちゃうかもしれないから～！　わたしたちのノートもお願いしていい？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4061
translate jp a1c8o1_142d50b9:

    # hi "Yeah."
    hi "ああ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4066
translate jp a1c8o1_23efa8d3:

    # mi "Perfect~! Yay~! Okay~! Thanks, Hicchan!"
    mi "最高～！　やったぁ～！　おっけ～！　ありがと、ひっちゃん！"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4072
translate jp a1c8o1_4e518d4d:

    # "They walk outside even though there are only ten minutes left before the bell will ring, signaling the start of class."
    "二人は外に出ていく。授業開始のベルが鳴るまであと１０分しかないのに。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4077
translate jp a1c8o2_90ed8436:

    # hi "Hey, I'm the new guy, remember?"
    hi "おい、俺は転校したばっかだってこと、憶えてるか？"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4079
translate jp a1c8o2_13b35597:

    # hi "It's not like I could've done much, even if I wanted."
    hi "いくら手伝いたくたって、大したことができるわけないだろ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4084
translate jp a1c8o2_2528f6c7:

    # li "That's right, you shouldn't expect a transfer student to jump right into it on his first week."
    li "その通りです。転校生が一週目からすぐ仕事に取りかかれると思うのは間違っていますよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4086
translate jp a1c8o2_ab1a1a07:

    # "Lilly taking my side feels oddly comforting so I decide to back her up too."
    "リリーが味方をしてくれると、なんだか心強い。俺もリリーの肩を持つことにしよう。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4088
translate jp a1c8o2_dff6816f:

    # hi "Yeah you're being unreasonable with us both."
    hi "そうだよ。俺たち両方に無茶を言ってるぞ、二人とも"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4093
translate jp a1c8o2_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4098
translate jp a1c8o2_c50c4cd5:

    # mi "Excuses, excuses. Miss Class Rep has had plenty of time to deal with her report."
    mi "はいはい、言い訳言い訳。学級委員さんは今までいくらでも申請書を書く時間があったはずよ"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4100
translate jp a1c8o2_62390796:

    # mi "And we repeatedly offered you a position to help with the student council work, but you refused to commit yourself to making the festival a success."
    mi "それにひっちゃん、あなたはこっちから何度も生徒会の仕事をしないかって誘ったのに断ったわね。学園祭の成功に貢献するチャンスだったのに"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4102
translate jp a1c8o2_3579514a:

    # hi "Yeah, but as I said back then, I'm not sure if…"
    hi "あのさ、前も言ったけど、そんなことできるかどうか……"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4104
translate jp a1c8o2_b708f32c:

    # "I don't have time for this right now; no matter what I do, it will mean being drawn into a confrontation with Shizune, and that is what she wants."
    "今はこんなことしてる場合じゃない。どうせ俺が何をしたって、静音との対立に引きずり込まれるだけだし、それが静音のねらいなんだ。"

# game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:4106
translate jp a1c8o2_d828bafd:

    # hi "Whatever. Forget it."
    hi "もういいよ。何でもない"

translate jp strings:

    # game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1120
    old "I don't understand why Shizune is suddenly getting mad at me."
    new "何で静音は突然俺に怒りだしたんだ。"

    # game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1120
    old "Don't drag me into this! I've done my part!"
    new "俺を巻き込むなよ！　自分のやれることはやった！"

    # game/script-a1-thursday.rpy:1120
    old "Hey, come on. Cut me and Lilly some slack…"
    new "なあ、頼むから。リリーを勘弁してやれよ……"

